(1, 1, 'Active Recall', 'active-recall', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Active Recall AI: Elevating Exam Success with AI Precision</h3>\n    <p>Active Recall AI stands as a revolutionary AI tool designed to propel success in exams and certifications. Its arsenal of features includes the automatic generation of quizzes and writing assignments from uploaded study material, creating a personalized and effective study experience.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Tailored Learning for Students of All Ages</h3>\n    <p>This versatile tool caters to students of all ages, offering a dynamic approach to learning that enhances understanding and confidence for upcoming assessments. Whether you\'re a high school student or a professional preparing for certifications, Active Recall AI adapts to your unique learning needs.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Empowering Exam Preparation: A Closer Look</h3>\n    <p>Active Recall AI becomes an indispensable companion for students preparing for exams. Take Emily, a high school student, for example. She uploads a book for study, and the AI generates multiple-choice questions based on the text. This not only enhances Emily\'s understanding but also prepares her for quizzes with precision.</p>\n    <p>For nursing students like Alexis, preparing for exams like the NCLEX-RN becomes more effective. Detailed source materials are uploaded, and Active Recall AI identifies crucial medical terminologies, creating essay questions based on practical medical scenarios. This unique approach helps Alexis apply theoretical knowledge to real-world situations, receiving targeted feedback for continuous improvement.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Professional Advancement with Active Recall AI</h3>\n    <p>Active Recall AI isn\'t limited to academic settings. Professionals aiming for certifications, such as AWS cloud architects, find immense value in this tool. Users like Jackson can upload study materials and prompt the system to create a tailored question bank that reflects the certification\'s structure.</p>\n    <p>Short essay questions challenge users like Jackson to architect solutions to real-world cloud scenarios, ensuring a deep understanding that goes beyond theoretical knowledge. The result is a targeted and effective preparation strategy for the certification exam.</p>\n</div>', 'High school exam preparation.\nStudy assistant to help with exam or certification preparation.\nQuiz generator to practice material and remember more of what you learn.', 'https://activerecall.com', NULL, 'https://activerecall.com/external/ar_favicon_32.png?v=3', 'active-recall-top.png', 'active-recall-middle.png', 'active-recall-bottom.png', 1, 0, 'free', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(2, 1, 'Learnmate', 'learnmate', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Exploring Learnmate: Revolutionizing Student Productivity</h3>\n    <p>Learnmate, a collaborative productivity tool meticulously crafted for students, stands at the forefront of educational innovation. This AI-integrated app redefines how students approach their studies, fostering efficiency and productivity in every academic endeavor.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Unleashing the Power of AI in Education</h3>\n    <p>At the core of Learnmate is cutting-edge AI integration, elevating it beyond a mere productivity tool. The inclusion of an AI tutor sets Learnmate apart, providing students with instant answers to questions and facilitating a deeper understanding of various subjects.</p>\n    <p>Learnmate goes beyond conventional productivity tools by offering a comprehensive suite of apps. From an AI writing tool to an assignment management feature, it\'s a holistic solution designed to streamline the academic journey.</p>\n    <p>This versatile tool seamlessly adapts to various devices, ensuring a consistent and user-friendly experience on PCs, tablets, and mobile devices. Remarkably, no software installations or updates are required, allowing students to focus on what matters most — their studies.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Key Features that Propel Learnmate</h3>\n    <ul>\n        <li>**Study Goals:** Learnmate empowers users to set and track study goals, providing a roadmap for academic success.</li>\n        <li>**Assignment Management:** Effectively manage assignments with Learnmate\'s intuitive tools, ensuring deadlines are met and tasks are organized.</li>\n        <li>**Collaboration:** Foster collaboration with peers through seamless features, promoting a collective approach to learning.</li>\n        <li>**Task Management:** Navigate academic responsibilities effortlessly with Learnmate\'s exceptional to-do lists, a game-changer in task management.</li>\n        <li>**Note-Taking Excellence:** Elevate your note-taking experience with Learnmate, offering a platform to create, share, and export study notes with ease.</li>\n    </ul>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">AI at the Heart of Learnmate</h3>\n    <p>The inclusion of an AI tutor in Learnmate transcends traditional learning boundaries. Students can pose questions and receive instant, accurate answers, enhancing comprehension and knowledge retention.</p>\n    <p>Moreover, the AI writing tool is a game-changer in academic writing. It assists students in crafting articulate essays and assignments, providing valuable insights to refine writing skills.</p>\n    <p>Assignment management becomes a breeze with Learnmate\'s AI-driven features. From organizing tasks to ensuring timely submissions, the tool becomes a virtual academic assistant.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Flexible Pricing Plans for Every Student</h3>\n    <p>Learnmate understands the diverse needs of students and offers flexible pricing plans. Higher-tier plans come with additional storage and premium features, allowing users to tailor their Learnmate experience to their unique requirements.</p>\n    <p>Getting started is risk-free with Learnmate\'s free trial. No credit card is required, and users enjoy the freedom to cancel at any time. This commitment to flexibility ensures that students can explore Learnmate\'s potential without constraints.</p>\n</div>', 'Efficient study goal setting and management.\nCollaborative study and assignment completion.\nStreamlining study routines and improving productivity.', 'https://learnmate.app/?via=studentaitools', NULL, 'https://learnmate.app/uploads/favicon/GtYAHDCIK7Hf2av15QUuOo