(3, 1, 'SchoolAI', 'schoolai', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Revolutionizing Teaching with SchoolAI</h3>\n    <p>SchoolAI, an innovative AI-powered tool crafted for educators, is set to redefine how teachers manage their daily tasks. From email-writing to lesson planning, marking, resource creation, and brainstorming, SchoolAI is a comprehensive solution designed to save valuable time and enhance productivity.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Personalized Efficiency at Your Fingertips</h3>\n    <p>One of SchoolAI\'s standout features is its ability to provide personalized results based on the unique preferences of each user. Tailored recommendations streamline tasks, ensuring that educators can focus on what matters most — teaching.</p>\n    <p>The inclusion of a time-saving counter adds another layer of efficiency. Teachers can track their productivity, fostering a sense of accomplishment and encouraging effective time management.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Comprehensive Task Management</h3>\n    <p>SchoolAI addresses various facets of a teacher\'s responsibilities, offering a multifaceted approach to task management. Whether it\'s drafting emails, marking assignments, planning lessons, or creating teaching resources, SchoolAI simplifies the process.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Support and Contact Feature</h3>\n    <p>Recognizing the importance of support, SchoolAI incorporates a dedicated feature for assistance and contact. Teachers can seamlessly access support when needed, ensuring a smooth experience with the tool.</p>\n</div>', 'Automated grading and feedback.\nPersonalized lesson planning.\nEfficient resource creation.', 'https://www.schoolai.co/?via=studentaitools', NULL, 'https://d1muf25xaso8