(10, 1, 'Whiteboard', 'whiteboard', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Unlocking Educational Potential with Whiteboard AI</h3>\n    <p>Whiteboard AI emerges as a comprehensive platform, ushering in a new era of educational tools. With a myriad of features and versatile use cases, it proves to be an indispensable companion for students seeking an interactive and enriching learning experience.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Key Features and Applications</h3>\n    <p>The Whiteboard AI tool stands out by offering a range of main features and versatile applications:</p>\n    <ul>\n        <li>**Interactive Summaries:** Generate interactive summaries that enhance comprehension and retention of key information.</li>\n        <li>**Time-Stamped Key Information:** Access time-stamped key information, providing a structured overview of lectures and learning materials.</li>\n        <li>**Instant Answers:** Receive instant answers to questions, promoting a dynamic and responsive learning environment.</li>\n    </ul>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Versatile Applications for Students</h3>\n    <p>Students can leverage the power of Whiteboard AI for various purposes:</p>\n    <ul>\n        <li>**Lecture Engagement:** Watch lectures, obtain interactive summaries, ask questions, and actively participate in the learning process.</li>\n        <li>**Collaboration:** Collaborate with peers, share insights, and bookmark important content for future reference.</li>\n        <li>**Preparation:** Efficiently prepare for classes with the aid of interactive learning materials and flashcards.</li>\n    </ul>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Transformative Capabilities of Whiteboard AI</h3>\n    <p>Whiteboard AI takes learning to the next level by