(18, 1, 'MindStudio', 'mindstudio', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">MindStudio YouAI: Revolutionizing AI Applications Without Code</h3>\n    <p>Embark on a journey of AI exploration with MindStudio YouAI, a formidable tool that empowers users to launch AI applications effortlessly, eliminating the need for coding expertise. Whether your aspirations involve content generators, utilities, enterprise apps, agents, characters, or bots, MindStudio YouAI is the comprehensive solution you\'ve been searching for.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Unlock Monthly Revenue with MindStudio YouAI</h3>\n    <p>A standout feature of MindStudio YouAI lies in its unique capability to help users generate monthly revenue. By implementing a straightforward monthly subscription model, you can monetize your AI creations and turn your passion into a lucrative venture. The tool provides a gateway for both creativity and financial success.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Seamless Onboarding in 15 Minutes</h3>\n    <p>Getting started with MindStudio YouAI is a breeze, requiring just 15 minutes to master its functionalities. The learning curve is designed with simplicity in mind, ensuring that users can swiftly navigate the tool and begin their AI journey without unnecessary complications.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Comprehensive Support and Resources</h3>\n    <p>If ever in need of assistance, MindStudio YouAI has you covered. Extensive documentation provides a detailed guide to the tool\'s features and functionalities. Additionally, video tutorials on YouTube offer visual insights, making the learning process even more accessible.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">User-Friendly Interface for Maximum Impact</h3>\n    <p>With a user-friendly interface, MindStudio YouAI ensures that unleashing the power of AI is not confined to coding experts. It democratizes access, allowing individuals from various backgrounds to harness the potential of AI without the complexities of coding.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Monetize Your AI Creativity</h3>\n    <p>Beyond its user-friendly nature, MindStudio YouAI stands out as a valuable tool for those aiming to monetize their AI endeavors. The monthly subscription model opens up new avenues for revenue, turning your AI applications into a sustainable source of income.</p>\n</div>', 'Build application without code.\nDevelop utilities and make money out of your creations.\nBuild simple tools and share them on the platform without code.\nCreate AI bots without code.', 'https://youai.ai/mindstudio?via=studentaitools', NULL, 'https://images.koji-cdn.com/generic/sCwYpl1OXYQxGtarpAaAevqh23R2_1675528797572.png?w=96&h=96', 'mindstudio-top.png', 'mindstudio-middle.png', 'mindstudio-bottom.png', 1, 0, 'free', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(19, 1, 'Ivyclub AI', 'ivyclub-ai', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Revolutionizing Graduate School Applications with Ivyclub AI</h3>\n    <p>Embarking on the journey to graduate school is a pivotal moment, and Ivyclub stands as the AI-powered ally that transforms this process. Specializing in crafting exceptional personal statements and resumes, Ivyclub AI is a game-changer in the competitive landscape of graduate school applications.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">AI-Powered Precision in Application Crafting</h3>\n    <p>Ivyclub AI leverages the power of artificial intelligence to elevate the quality of personal statements and resumes. It goes beyond traditional tools by learning from successful applications to top schools. This unique feature enables users to create documents that stand out, tailored to their specific program and infused with a distinctive flair.</p>\n    <p>Say goodbye to generic templates and clichés. Ivyclub AI generates drafts that are refreshingly unique, ensuring that your application materials leave a lasting impression.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Comprehensive Features for Application Excellence</h3>\n    <p>Aside from its advanced drafting capabilities, Ivyclub AI offers a suite of features to enhance every aspect of your application:</p>\n    <ul>\n        <li>**Rephrasing:** Fine-tune your content with intelligent rephrasing tools.</li>\n        <li>**Grammar Checking:** Ensure impeccable language with robust grammar checking functionalities.</li>\n        <li>**Translation Tools:** Break language barriers with translation tools for international students.</li>\n        <li>**Revision Assistance:** Access a vast database of successful graduate school applications for expert reviews and improvement suggestions.</li>\n    </ul>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Tailored Assistance for Every Applicant</h3>\n    <p>Whether you\'re a busy professional, an international student navigating language nuances, or someone seeking guidance in the application process, Ivyclub AI is the solution. Its user-friendly interface and powerful features make it accessible to a diverse range of applicants, ensuring that everyone receives the support they need.</p>\n</div>', 'Create personal statements that standout for different schools.\nCraft professional and reviewed resumes and CV with AI writing assistance.\nWrite statements of purpose that are unique and compelling in minutes.', 'https://ivyclub.ai?via=studentaitools', NULL, 'https://ivyclub.ai/favicon.ico', 'ivyclub-ai-top.png', 'ivyclub-ai-middle.png', 'ivyclub-ai-bottom.png', 1, 0, 'free', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(20, 1, 'Roughly', 'roughly', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Exploring Roughly: Turning Dreams into Art with AI</h3>\n    <p>Roughly, an innovative AI tool, stands as a beacon for individuals seeking to transform their dreams into tangible works of art effortlessly. This cutting-edge application redefines the creative process, catering to both seasoned artists and beginners alike.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Seamless Artistic Expression for All</h3>\n    <p>With Roughly, the creation of stunning artwork becomes an intuitive experience. The tool\'s user-friendly interface encourages users to draw and sketch with the carefree spirit of a child, while simultaneously offering advanced features for those aspiring to produce professional-level designs.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">From Novice to Pro: Bridging the Gap with Advanced Features</h3>\n    <p>Roughly transcends the limitations of traditional art tools by providing a platform where users can embrace their artistic journey at their own pace. Whether you\'re experimenting with your first strokes or aiming for intricate designs, Roughly is designed to meet your artistic needs.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Versatility Redefined: Roughly for Every Industry</h3>\n    <p>Roughly isn\'t confined to a specific use case; instead, it emerges as a versatile tool with applications across various industries. Architects can craft captivating building designs, fashion designers can visualize stunning outfits, game developers can design characters and landscapes, and movie producers can conceptualize scenes — all within the expansive canvas of Roughly.</p>\n</div>', 'Visualize architectural design.\nDraw fashion designs and more.\nArt collaboration.', 'https://www.roughly.app/?via=studentaitools', NULL, 'https://assets.website-files.com/644d4409f379b21fcf2bf2d2/644d91028242dcfbd1208d99_Roughly-32.gif', 'roughly-top.png', 'roughly-middle.png', 'roughly-bottom.png', 1, 0, 'free', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(21, 1, 'CourseFactory AI CoPilot', 'coursefactory-ai-copilot', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">CourseFactory AI CoPilot: Transforming Online Course Creation</h3>\n    <p>CourseFactory AI CoPilot emerges as the pinnacle of innovation in online course creation, introducing an AI-powered assistant that redefines the entire process, making it not just faster but remarkably efficient. Tailored for teachers, trainers, and coaches, CourseFactory\'s team of AI agents is dedicated to guiding users from the course\'s conceptualization to content generation and insightful student feedback analysis.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Revolutionizing Course Creation</h3>\n    <p>Imagine creating a comprehensive course in a fraction of the time it traditionally takes. CourseFactory AI CoPilot turns this imagination into reality. Collaborate seamlessly with our AI agents, ensuring that your unique teaching vision is brought to life while preserving your personal touch. Recognizing the individuality of every educator, CourseFactory empowers them to craft courses that reflect their distinct style.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Customization at Your Fingertips</h3>\n    <p>CourseFactory AI CoPilot offers a user-friendly platform to customize courses according to your teaching style and the unique needs of your students. Rapidly craft high-quality courses that align with learning objectives, creating an immersive and enriched learning experience for your students.</p>\n</div>', 'Faster online course creation for your students, employees or customers.\nEfficient course content generation on any topic.\nMaintain course quality while speeding up the workflow and creation process.', 'https://coursefactory.ai/?via=studentaitools', NULL, 'https://static.tildacdn.com/tild6261-3235-4961-b335-356264393038/favicon.ico', 'coursefactory-ai-copilot-top.png', 'coursefactory-ai-copilot-middle.png', 'coursefactory-ai-copilot-bottom.png', 1, 0, 'free', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(22, 1, 'YouAI', 'youai', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Unlocking Possibilities with YouAI: A Comprehensive AI Ecosystem</h3>\n    <p>YouAI stands out as a versatile collection of AI applications, offering a diverse range of functionalities under one unified platform. From content creation and writing to teaching, education, business, job seeking, and everyday life, YouAI caters to a myriad of needs.</p>\n    <p>What sets YouAI apart is its user-centric approach, empowering individuals to create powerful AI applications tailored to their unique requirements in less than a minute. This streamlined process revolutionizes how users interact with AI technology, making it accessible and efficient.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">A Glimpse into YouAI\'s Capabilities</h3>\n    <p>YouAI\'s scope is vast, offering solutions across various domains:</p>\n    <ul>\n        <li>**Content Creation and Writing:** Elevate your writing experience with AI-powered assistants that enhance creativity and efficiency.</li>\n        <li>**Teaching and Education:** Explore innovative AI applications that redefine the learning experience for both educators and students.</li>\n        <li>**Business Solutions:** YouAI provides tools for businesses, leveraging AI for enhanced productivity and strategic decision-making.</li>\n        <li>**Job Seekers:** Navigate the job market with AI-driven assistance, from resume building to interview preparation.</li>\n        <li>**Everyday Life:** Experience the convenience of AI in daily tasks, from health and wellness apps to personalized assistants.</li>\n    </ul>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Empowering Users with Rapid AI App Creation</h3>\n    <p>YouAI revolutionizes the way individuals interact with AI technology by placing the power of app creation in their