(23, 1, 'TutorMind', 'tutormind', NULL, 'Tutor Mind is an AI-powered tool that simplifies teaching by providing features such as lesson planning, essay checking, question generation, and plagiarism detection for teachers. It is designed to save time and make the workload easier for teachers, providing quality education. It offers four powerful tools to save hundreds of hours by allowing teachers to plan lessons, mark essays, and detect plagiarism quickly and easily. The tool also includes an advanced AI detector to check past student texts for authenticity instantly. Tutor Mind also provides an optimized large-screen mode for an excellent user experience.', 'Simplify lesson planning.\nCheck essays for plagiarism.\nGenerate questions for assessments.', 'https://www.tutor-mind.com/?via=studentaitools', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 'free', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(24, 1, 'Chat2course', 'chat2course', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Revolutionizing Learning: Unveiling the Power of AI</h3>\n    <p>Embark on a transformative learning journey with an AI tool designed to redefine the educational landscape. This innovative platform offers customizable learning experiences, combining a personal course builder with the guidance of an AI tutor to empower users in mastering their desired skills.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Tailored Learning at Your Fingertips</h3>\n    <p>Experience the future of education with this AI tool\'s customizable learning features. The personal course builder allows users to shape their learning path according to their goals, while the AI tutor provides personalized guidance for a more enriching learning experience.</p>\n    <p>Discover the convenience of AI-curated course selections and human collaboration features that bring personalized learning to your fingertips. It\'s not just a tool; it\'s a companion in your educational journey.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Diverse Course Offerings for Holistic Learning</h3>\n    <p>Delve into a diverse range of courses covering health and wellness, women\'s hormonal health, mind-body connection, intermittent fasting, and immune system boosting. This AI tool serves as a comprehensive repository of knowledge, ensuring that users have access to courses that cater to their holistic well-being.</p>\n    <p>Engage actively in the learning process with interactive activities embedded throughout the courses. It\'s not just about acquiring knowledge; it\'s about immersing yourself in a dynamic and participatory learning environment.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Crafting Your Learning Experience</h3>\n    <p>Unlock the full potential of personalized learning with features designed to cater to individual preferences. The tool provides a chat feature that assists users in crafting a course overview and generates a customized learning plan based on their unique preferences and aspirations.</p>\n</div>', 'Mastering any topic with building personalized courses.\nBuild courses for your organization or website..\nCreate personalized learning plans for any topic based on learning style.\nEngage into self paced learning for any skill you want.', 'https://chat2course.com/?via=studentaitools', NULL, NULL, 'chat2course-top.png', 'chat2course-middle.png', 'chat2course-bottom.png', 1, 0, 'free', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(25, 1, 'Magictool.AI', 'magictool.ai', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Unleashing Productivity: Exploring MagicTool.AI</h3>\n    <p>Embark on a journey of unparalleled productivity with MagicTool.AI, a revolutionary solution that consolidates 20 distinct AI capabilities into one comprehensive subscription. Bid farewell to the hassle of switching between tools – MagicTool.AI is your all-in-one solution, streamlining tasks and offering a plethora of features under a single umbrella.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">A Symphony of Features</h3>\n    <p>MagicTool.AI encompasses an array of features that cater to various aspects of your workflow:</p>\n    <ul>\n        <li>**ChatGPT Conversations:** Engage in dynamic conversations with ChatGPT, unlocking a world of possibilities for interactive and productive discussions.</li>\n        <li>**Web Page Summarization:** Quickly summarize web pages, saving valuable time and ensuring you grasp essential information efficiently.</li>\n        <li>**PDF Interaction via Chat:** Seamlessly interact with PDFs through chat, enhancing collaboration and document handling.</li>\n        <li>**Text Explanations:** Receive detailed explanations of text, fostering better understanding and clarity in your reading material.</li>\n        <li>**Grammar Checking:** Elevate your writing with built-in grammar checking, ensuring your content is polished and error-free.</li>\n        <li>**Text Quality Enhancement:** Enhance the quality of your text, making it more impactful and engaging for your audience.</li>\n        <li>**Language Simplification:** Simplify complex language, catering to diverse audiences and enhancing communication.</li>\n        <li>**Text Length Adjustment:** Tailor your text length to meet specific requirements, whether it\'s for social media or formal documents.</li>\n        <li>**Content Paraphrasing:** Effortlessly paraphrase content, maintaining originality while meeting different stylistic needs.</li>\n        <li>**Information Summarization:** Condense large volumes of information into concise summaries, extracting key insights efficiently.</li>\n        <li>**Maintaining Writing Flow:** Keep your writing flow intact with features designed to enhance the continuity of your content.</li>\n        <li>**Adding Emojis:** Infuse personality into your text by easily incorporating emojis, adding a touch of flair to your communication.</li>\n        <li>**Google Translation:** Break language barriers with Google translation capabilities, ensuring your content reaches a global audience.</li>\n        <li>**AI-Generated Images:** Access a library of AI-generated images to complement your content and make it visually appealing.</li>\n        <li>**Note-Taking:** Streamline your note-taking process, making it efficient and organized for better knowledge retention.</li>\n        <li>**String Manipulation:** Easily manipulate strings to meet specific formatting or data processing needs.</li>\n        <li>**GPT-4 Access (in Pro Plans):** Unlock the power of GPT-4, accessing advanced AI capabilities to elevate your creative and analytical endeavors.</li>\n        <li>**Magic Editor:** Leverage the Magic Editor for seamless content creation and editing, simplifying complex tasks.</li>\n        <li>**Magic Shortcut:** Enjoy the convenience of the Magic Shortcut, a tool designed to optimize and expedite your workflow.</li>\n    </ul>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">A Tool for Every Need</h3>\n    <p>MagicTool.AI emerges as the ultimate all-in-one tool for writing, content creation, and workflow optimization. It\'s not just a tool; it\'s a companion in your journey to boost productivity and efficiency. Experience the magic of streamlined tasks and elevated creativity with MagicTool.AI.</p>\n</div>', 'Efficient