(26, 1, 'Yomu AI', 'yomu-ai', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Yomu AI: Elevating Academic Writing with Artificial Intelligence</h3>\n    <p>Yomu AI stands as a beacon of innovation in the realm of academic writing, offering an AI-powered writing assistant that transforms the writing experience. Tailored to assist students and academics, Yomu AI is a trusted companion in the journey to crafting superior essays and academic papers.</p>\n    <p>Universities and academic labs worldwide vouch for the efficacy of Yomu AI, making it a go-to tool for those seeking excellence in their written work. Its versatile capabilities encompass everything from brainstorming to the meticulous task of including citations, all designed to streamline the writing process.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Unleashing the Power of Yomu AI</h3>\n    <ul>\n        <li>**Time-saving Excellence:** Yomu AI is a time-saving marvel, empowering users to write superior papers with ease and efficiency.</li>\n        <li>**Trusted by Academia:** The widespread trust of universities and academic labs globally underscores the reliability and excellence embedded in Yomu AI.</li>\n        <li>**Versatile Assistance:** Yomu AI goes beyond traditional writing tools. It assists in brainstorming, refining, paraphrasing, expanding, shortening, summarizing, and transforming bullet points into detailed, coherent text.</li>\n    </ul>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">AI-Powered Citation Mastery</h3>\n    <p>Yomu AI redefines how citations are handled in academic writing. With its AI-powered citation tool, the once daunting task of finding, including, and formatting citations is now effortless. Powered by Sourcely technology, Yomu AI ensures accuracy and precision in every citation.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Preserving Originality and Academic Integrity</h3>\n    <p>One of the cornerstones of Yomu AI\'s design is its commitment to maintaining originality and upholding academic integrity. Users can confidently navigate the writing process, knowing that Yomu AI is a dedicated partner in ensuring that the work remains authentic and aligned with academic standards.</p>\n</div>', 'Assisting in writing essays, research papers, and grants.\nProviding suggestions and feedback on writing specially academic papers with citations.\nEditing and improving papers with brainstorming, paraphrasing, and summarizing.', 'https://www.yomu.ai/?via=studentaitools', NULL, 'https://www.yomu.ai/favicon.ico', 'yomu-ai-top.png', 'yomu-ai-middle.png', 'yomu-ai-bottom.png', 1, 0, 'free', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(27, 1, 'Aspect', 'aspect', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Revolutionizing Interviews with Aspect AI</h3>\n    <p>Aspect AI emerges as a transformative tool that turns interviews into a strategic advantage. By eliminating the need for constant note-taking, Aspect allows users to delve deep into conversations, focusing entirely on the interaction. The tool leverages human-level AI to generate detailed, custom summaries that capture the nuances essential for strategic decision-making.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Key Features of Aspect AI</h3>\n    <ul>\n        <li>**Human-Level AI Notes:** Aspect provides AI-generated notes that reflect the subtleties of each conversation, ensuring a comprehensive understanding.</li>\n        <li>**Interviewer Feedback:** Receive personalized feedback on your interviewing technique, enabling continuous improvement based on real interactions.</li>\n        <li>**ATS Integration:** Seamlessly integrate Aspect with your existing ATS systems for an end-to-end hiring solution, enhancing productivity and visibility into hiring stats.</li>\n        <li>**Highlight Reels:** Create short highlight reels for efficient team collaboration and faster decision-making.</li>\n        <li>**Transcription Excellence:** Stand out with Aspect\'s superior transcription capabilities, delivering impeccable grammar and syntax.</li>\n        <li>**Responsive Support:** The Aspect team is prompt, helpful, and accessible, ensuring a positive user experience.</li>\n    </ul>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">ATS Integration: A Game-Changer in Hiring</h3>\n    <p>Aspect\'s seamless integration with existing ATS systems revolutionizes the hiring process. This enhancement eliminates context-switching stress, boosts productivity, and provides comprehensive insights into hiring statistics. Recruiters have hailed the ATS integration as a game-changer, ushering in faster and more efficient hiring processes.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Faster Decision-Making with Aspect</h3>\n    <p>Aspect empowers users to make faster and informed decisions through its AI-powered insights. The ability to create highlight reels facilitates swift collaboration within teams and with clients, streamlining the decision-making process.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Superior Note-Taking Platform</h3>\n    <p>Aspect not only excels in interview facilitation but also serves as an exceptional note-taking platform. Its transcription capabilities set a new standard in terms of grammar and syntax, ensuring accurate and polished documentation.</p>\n    <p>With Aspect, recruiters and hiring managers are liberated from the constraints of note-taking, allowing for complete engagement with candidates. The tool\'s automatic interview recording and human-level AI notes significantly enhance the efficiency of the hiring process, leading to better hiring decisions.</p>\n</div>', 'Streamlining the hiring process.\nImproving interviewing technique.\nCreating custom interview summaries.\nBoosting productivity in recruitment.', 'https://aspect-hq.com/?via=studentaitools', NULL, 'https://framerusercontent.com/images/tqMxQ4YbgibMJ1mKgQx3asTgUDw.png', 'aspect-top.png', 'aspect-middle.png', 'aspect-bottom.png', 1, 0, 'free', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(28, 1, 'Scholarcy', 'scholarcy', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Unlocking Efficiency with Scholarcy: A Summarizing Marvel</h3>\n    <p>Scholarcy emerges as a transformative online summarizing tool, offering a rapid solution for distilling lengthy texts. Leveraging advanced AI techniques, it excels in extracting main points and crucial information from extensive documents, providing users with a comprehensive understanding in a matter of minutes.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">AI-Powered Summarization for Diverse Use Cases</h3>\n    <p>At the heart of Scholarcy\'s prowess is its utilization of AI, making it a versatile tool with myriad applications. Users can harness its power for:</p>\n    <ul>\n        <li>**Summarizing Articles, Reports, and Books:** Scholarcy simplifies the process of condensing lengthy publications, making information consumption efficient.</li>\n        <li>**Extracting Key Points and Definitions:** Users can swiftly extract essential elements from complex texts, aiding in focused learning and research.</li>\n        <li>**Highlighting Important Information:** Scholarcy identifies and highlights critical information, ensuring users don\'t miss key details in the vast sea of content.</li>\n        <li>**Generating Interactive Summary Flashcards:** Elevate your study sessions with interactive flashcards, created effortlessly through Scholarcy\'s intelligent summarization.</li>\n    </ul>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">User-Friendly Summarization at Your Fingertips</h3>\n    <p>Scholarcy\'s user interface is designed for simplicity without compromising functionality. Users can navigate the tool effortlessly, making it accessible to both novices and seasoned researchers. The power of AI-driven summarization is at your fingertips, redefining how we interact with and comprehend extensive textual content.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Effortless Summarization with Scholarcy</h3>\n    <p>Scholarcy\'s modus operandi involves streamlining the summarization process, ensuring that users save time without sacrificing the essence of the content. Its intelligent algorithms analyze text structures, identify key concepts, and present a coherent summary that captures the essence of the original document.</p>\n    <p>Whether you\'re a student needing to distill research papers or a professional requiring quick insights from reports, Scholarcy proves to be an indispensable companion in your quest for efficiency.</p>\n</div>', 'Summarizing articles, reports, and books.\nExtracting key points and definitions.\nGenerating interactive summary flashcards.', 'https://www.scholarcy.com/?via=studentaitools', NULL, 'https://www.scholarcy.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/cropped-Scholarcy-logo-main-32x32.png', 'scholarcy-top.png', 'scholarcy-middle.png', 'scholarcy-bottom.png', 1, 0, 'free', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(29, 1, 'Mimir', 'mimir', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Unlocking Mentorship with Mimir: Your AI Companion for Guidance</h3>\n    <p>Embark on a journey of knowledge and growth with Mimir, an innovative AI tool designed to connect you with mentors and provide invaluable advice. This revolutionary platform employs AI personalities to ensure precise mentor matches, creating a space where seeking guidance is both accessible and enriching.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">The Essence of Mimir\'s AI-driven Mentorship</h3>\n    <p>Mimir\'s unique approach to mentorship leverages AI personalities, adding a layer of sophistication to the matching process. This ensures that users are paired with mentors who can offer relevant insights and guidance based on their individual needs and aspirations.</p>\n    <p>One standout feature of Mimir is its ability to learn from your previous queries. This means that as you engage with mentors and seek advice, the AI adapts to your preferences, enabling each interaction to be more tailored and valuable than the last.</p>\n    <p>Notably, Mimir eliminates the need for an expansive network or costly platform subscriptions. It envisions a democratized mentorship landscape where seeking advice is not restricted by financial barriers or the need for extensive professional networks.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Navigating Mimir\'s User-Friendly Experience</h3>\n    <p>Mimir prioritizes simplicity and accessibility. The user-friendly interface ensures that connecting with mentors and seeking advice is a seamless process. There\'s no need to navigate complex networks or spend money on a dedicated platform.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Revolutionizing Q&A with Mimir\'s Adaptive Approach</h3>\n    <p>Engage in meaningful Q&A sessions with mentors on Mimir\'s platform. The AI\'s ability to understand your previous queries enhances the quality of advice you receive. It\'s a dynamic and evolving process where each interaction contributes to a more personalized and enriching experience.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Mimir: No Networks, No Costs, Just Mentorship</h3>\n    <p>Unlike traditional mentorship platforms, Mimir breaks free from the constraints of networks and costs. It envisions a world where mentorship is a fundamental right, accessible to anyone with the desire to learn and grow.</p>\n</div>', 'Find a mentor for career advice.\nGet guidance on personal development.\nAsk for feedback on a project.', 'https://www.withmimir.com/?via=studentaitools', NULL, 'https://www.withmimir.com/favicon.svg', 'mimir-top.png', 'mimir-middle.png', 'mimir-bottom.png', 1, 0, 'free', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(30, 1, 'PerfectEssayWriterAI', 'perfectessaywriterai', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">The Revolution of Essay Writing: AI Essay Writer</h3>\n    <p>Introducing the AI Essay Writer, a groundbreaking AI-powered writing tool crafted to revolutionize how students create high-quality essays effortlessly and promptly. This tool encompasses a suite of features, including an essay writer, outline generator, citation generator, topic generator, thesis statement generator, and a grammar and style checker.</p>\n    <p>At its core, the AI Essay Writer leverages the power of natural language processing and machine learning. This enables the tool to adapt to the unique writing style and requirements of each student, providing personalized and precise results tailored to individual needs.</p>\n    <p>Key tools embedded in this AI-powered writing marvel are strategically designed to streamline the entire writing process. By doing so, students can save valuable time and effort, focusing more on the substance of their work rather than the mechanics of writing.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Features for Academic Excellence</h3>\n    <ul>\n        <li>**Efficient Essay Writing:** The essay writer component ensures that students can effortlessly generate well-crafted essays with ease and speed.</li>\n        <li>**Structured Outlines:** Benefit from the outline generator, providing a roadmap for a well-organized and coherent essay structure.</li>\n        <li>**Accurate Citations:** The citation generator simplifies the often tedious task of creating accurate citations, adhering to various citation styles.</li>\n        <li>**Inspiring Topics:** Find inspiration with the topic generator, sparking creativity and helping students explore diverse subject matter.</li>\n        <li>**Robust Thesis Statements:** Craft powerful thesis statements effortlessly with the dedicated thesis statement generator.</li>\n        <li>**Polished Grammar:** The grammar and style checker ensures that every piece of writing adheres to grammatical excellence and a consistent style.</li>\n    </ul>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Personalized Assistance and Continuous Improvement</h3>\n    <p>The AI Essay Writer places a strong emphasis on personalized assistance, understanding that each student\'s writing journey is unique. Through continuous improvement, the tool evolves to meet the changing needs of students, ensuring it remains a reliable companion in their academic pursuits.</p>\n    <p>Moreover, the tool is designed with a user-friendly interface, enhancing the overall writing experience. Its intuitive design promotes efficiency and ease of use, making it accessible to students at all levels.</p>\n</div>', 'Assisting students in generating high-quality essays.\nStreamlining the writing process for students.\nProviding personalized assistance and accurate results.', 'https://www.perfectessaywriter.ai/?via=studentaitools', NULL, 'https://www.perfectessaywriter.ai/images/pew-fav-icon.png', 'perfectessaywriterai-top.png', 'perfectessaywriterai-middle.png', 'perfectessaywriterai-bottom.png', 1, 0, 'free', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(31, 1, 'EssayGrader', 'essaygrader', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Revolutionizing Essay Grading with EssayGrad</h3>\n    <p>EssayGrad emerges as a groundbreaking AI-powered tool dedicated to transforming the essay grading landscape. Tailored to meet the needs of educators, this tool brings forth unparalleled efficiency and accuracy in evaluating essays.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">AI-Powered Precision in Feedback</h3>\n    <p>At the core of EssayGrad is its powerful AI engine, capable of providing specific and accurate feedback based on predefined rubrics. This sophisticated system identifies areas in an essay that require improvement, offering valuable insights to both teachers and students.</p>\n    <p>Teachers benefit from a concise summary generated by EssayGrad, streamlining the grading process and enabling more focused guidance for students striving to enhance their writing skills.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Comprehensive Features for Enhanced Grading</h3>\n    <p>EssayGrad goes beyond traditional grading tools with its innovative features:</p>\n    <ul>\n        <li>**AI Detector:** Uncover essays written by AI with the tool\'s AI detector, ensuring academic integrity is maintained.</li>\n        <li>**Error Report:** Addressing grammar, spelling, and punctuation errors, the error report feature elevates the quality of feedback provided by EssayGrad.</li>\n    </ul>\n    <p>The collective aim is to revolutionize essay grading, making it not only faster but significantly more accurate, ultimately benefiting both teachers and students.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Continuous Improvement with Regular Updates</h3>\n    <p>EssayGrad is committed to staying at the forefront of technological advancements. Continuous updates ensure that educators have access to the latest features and improvements, further enhancing the grading experience.</p>\n    <p>The availability of a free version allows educators to explore the tool\'s capabilities without financial commitment, making it an accessible and valuable resource in the realm of education technology.</p>\n</div>', 'Accelerate essay grading process for teachers.\nProvide accurate feedback to students.\nIdentify AI-generated essays.', 'https://essaygrader.ai/?via=studentaitools', NULL, 'https://essaygrader.ai/favicon.ico', 'essaygrader-top.png', 'essaygrader-middle.png', 'essaygrader-bottom.png', 1, 0, 'free', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(32, 1, 'Masterpiece Studio', 'masterpiece-studio', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Revolutionizing 3D Modeling with AI: A Dive into Innovative Technology</h3>\n    <p>Embark on a journey of innovation as we explore how the AI tool is reshaping the landscape of 3D model generation. This cutting-edge technology simplifies the intricate process of creating, editing, and deploying highly usable 3D models, offering a game-changing solution for both gaming enthusiasts and professionals in the 3D application domain.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">The Three Stages of AI-Powered 3D Model Creation</h3>\n    <p>The AI tool functions seamlessly in three key stages, each contributing to the creation of compelling 3D assets:</p>\n    <ul>\n        <li>**Content Generation:** Experience the magic of AI as it generates intricate 3D content, laying the foundation for stunning visual experiences.</li>\n        <li>**Content Editing and Refinement:** Dive into the creative process with powerful editing tools that allow users to refine and perfect their 3D creations.</li>\n        <li>**3D Asset Deployment:** Witness the seamless deployment of 3D assets, ready to enhance games and various 3D applications.</li>\n    </ul>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Empowering Creativity and Opening Economic Avenues</h3>\n    <p>At its core, the company behind this AI tool envisions a future where individuals can unleash their creativity without barriers. By simplifying 3D content creation, the tool empowers users to expand their capabilities and explore new economic opportunities in the dynamic world of 3D modeling.</p>\n</div>', 'Create 3D models for video games.\nGenerate 3D models for architectural visualization.\nProduce 3D models for product design.', 'https://masterpiecestudio.com/blog/3d-generative-ai?via=studentaitools', NULL, 'https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/602d51578708e920ebe66bf7/23a1ece6-d982-4969-a69c-e8c964eef384/favicon.ico', 'masterpiece-studio-top.png', 'masterpiece-studio-middle.png', 'masterpiece-studio-bottom.png', 1, 0, 'free', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(33, 1, 'Praxy AI', 'praxy-ai', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Unveiling Praxi AI: Empowering Students with AI Excellence</h3>\n    <p>Praxi AI emerges as a formidable AI-powered tool, designed to empower students across various academic pursuits. This multifaceted solution introduces a Chrome extension, redefining how students engage with educational content.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">A Glimpse into Praxi AI\'s Arsenal</h3>\n    <p>Praxi AI stands out with a rich set of features, each meticulously crafted to enhance the student experience:</p>\n    <ul>\n        <li>**AI-Powered Tutor:** Experience a virtual tutor at your fingertips, leveraging AI for instant clarification and guidance.</li>\n        <li>**Search Engine:** Navigate through vast realms of information effortlessly with Praxi AI\'s intelligent search capabilities.</li>\n        <li>**Summarizer:** Condense lengthy articles or documents into concise summaries, saving time without compromising comprehension.</li>\n        <li>**Paraphrasing Tool:** Master the art of paraphrasing with a tool that ensures your writing is both original and impactful.</li>\n        <li>**Note-Taking Excellence:** Elevate your note-taking game with a feature-rich tool that goes beyond traditional methods.</li>\n    </ul>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Seamless Exploration with a Free Trial</h3>\n    <p>Praxi AI invites users to embark on a risk-free exploration of its capabilities. The tool offers a free trial without the need for credit card details, allowing students to experience its potential without any upfront commitment.</p>\n    <p>Devoid of marketing fluff and pricing intricacies in this extract, Praxi AI places emphasis on the user\'s experience, encouraging a genuine interaction with the tool\'s offerings.</p>\n</div>', 'Improve study efficiency with AI-powered summarizer and note-taking feature.\nGet personalized help with AI-powered tutor.\nQuickly find relevant information with AI-powered search engine.', 'https://praxis-ai.com/?via=studentaitools', NULL, 'https://praxis-ai.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/cropped-praxis-favicon-180x180.png', 'praxy-ai-top.png', 'praxy-ai-middle.png', 'praxy-ai-bottom.png', 1, 0, 'free', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(34, 1, 'Aistote', 'aistote', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Aistot: Revolutionizing Study Sessions with AI</h3>\n    <p>Meet Aistot, the AI-powered tool designed to transform the studying experience. Aistot takes studying on-the-go to the next level by generating question flashcards and course content, ensuring that learning is not bound by a specific time or place.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Seamless Accessibility Across Devices</h3>\n    <p>Aistot caters to the diverse tech landscape, making it accessible on Android, Windows, and iOS devices. Its versatility extends to popular social media platforms such as Instagram, TikTok, and Twitter, allowing users to integrate learning seamlessly into their social media routines.</p>\n    <p>The user-friendly interface of Aistot enhances accessibility, and its synchronization feature ensures a consistent experience across multiple devices. Whether on a smartphone, tablet, or computer, users can pick up right where they left off.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Empowering Educators with Aistot</h3>\n    <p>Teachers, too, find Aistot to be a valuable ally in their quest for efficient teaching. The tool enables educators to swiftly create quizzes and flashcards, saving precious time in lesson preparation. This feature-rich platform fosters an interactive and engaging learning environment for both teachers and students.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Key Features of Aistot</h3>\n    <ul>\n        <li>**Question Flashcards:** Aistot\'s AI generates dynamic question flashcards, enhancing the memorization and understanding of course content.</li>\n        <li>**Multi-Device Sync:** Seamlessly switch between devices with Aistot\'s synchronization feature, ensuring a continuous and uninterrupted learning experience.</li>\n        <li>**Social Media Integration:** Integrate learning into your social media routine with Aistot\'s compatibility with Instagram, TikTok, and Twitter.</li>\n        <li>**Effortless Quiz Creation:** Teachers can create quizzes and flashcards swiftly, optimizing their time for more effective teaching.</li>\n    </ul>\n</div>', 'Create study materials on-the-go.\nQuickly generate quizzes and flashcards for students.\nEfficiently learn and retain information.', 'https://bento.me/aistote?via=studentaitools', NULL, 'https://creatorspace.imgix.net/users/cle6hepi301ohnf0yozucll5u/tBvgKhPdI3nw051x-original.png?w=200&h=200&fit=crop', 'aistote-top.png', 'aistote-middle.png', 'aistote-bottom.png', 1, 0, 'free', NULL, NULL, NULL);
