(35, 1, 'Jagoda', 'jagoda', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Revolutionizing Learning with Jagoda.ai</h3>\n    <p>Jagoda.ai stands as a beacon in the realm of online tutoring, powered by advanced AI to deliver personalized assistance across a spectrum of subjects. From mathematics to biology and chemistry, Jagoda.ai is your go-to tool for solving homework problems with ease and precision.</p>\n    <p>Using Jagoda.ai is a seamless experience — upload a photo or type in your question directly, and watch as the tool provides step-by-step solutions. Its versatility extends to language accessibility, offering support in over 20 languages to accommodate students with diverse linguistic backgrounds.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Tailored Learning with Jagoda.ai</h3>\n    <p>Jagoda.ai distinguishes itself by its remarkable ability to adapt to your unique learning style. It goes beyond generic solutions by considering your school and grade level, ensuring that the provided solutions align with your current curriculum. This tailored approach enhances the effectiveness of the learning experience.</p>\n    <p>Not fluent in German? No problem. Jagoda.ai is designed to be inclusive, providing support in multiple languages to bridge linguistic gaps and make learning accessible to a global audience.</p>\n    <p>Have follow-up questions? Jagoda.ai encourages inquisitiveness by allowing you to ask additional questions, deepening your understanding of the problems at hand.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Self-Directed Learning Made Easy</h3>\n    <p>Jagoda.ai is not just a tutoring tool; it\'s a proponent of self-directed learning. Empowering students to independently tackle assignments, it acts as a guiding AI tutor, offering assistance while allowing you to take charge of your academic journey.</p>\n    <p>The tool\'s comprehensive explanations and practice exercises for each topic contribute to a holistic learning experience, aiming not just to solve immediate problems but to enhance overall academic performance.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">User-Friendly Excellence</h3>\n    <p>Jagoda.ai excels not only in functionality but also in user-friendliness. Its intuitive platform ensures that students can easily navigate and utilize its features for personalized tutoring assistance. The tool\'s commitment to supporting various learning styles and languages makes it a versatile and indispensable asset for students worldwide.</p>\n</div>', 'Get personalized assistance for various subjects that consider your grades.\nReceive step-by-step solutions for homework problems.\nImprove grades with tailored feedback and practice exercises.', 'https://www.jagoda.ai?via=studentaitools', NULL, 'https://www.jagoda.ai/assets/img/favicon/favicon.ico', 'jagoda-top.png', 'jagoda-middle.png', 'jagoda-bottom.png', 1, 0, 'free', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(36, 1, 'Khan Academy Khanmigo', 'khan-academy-khanmigo', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Revolutionizing Education with Khanmigo AI</h3>\n    <p>Step into the future of education with Khanmigo AI, a groundbreaking tool that brings personalized tutoring to students and valuable insights to teachers. This tool, covering various subject areas, including the dynamic field of computer science, is set to redefine the learning experience.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Empowering Students and Educators</h3>\n    <p>Khanmigo AI invites users to join the waitlist, offering them a unique opportunity to test the tool and contribute valuable feedback. This collaborative approach ensures that the tool evolves to meet the diverse needs of its users, providing a tailor-made educational experience.</p>\n    <p>As part of Khan Academy, a nonprofit organization dedicated to providing free education resources globally, Khanmigo AI reflects a commitment to accessible education. The tool stands as a testament to the organization\'s mission of making quality education available to everyone, everywhere.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Supporting Educational Initiatives</h3>\n    <p>Donations are a vital aspect of Khanmigo\'s development and the creation of other online education resources. By contributing, users play a direct role in shaping the future of education, ensuring that innovative tools like Khanmigo continue to thrive and benefit learners worldwide.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Pilot Phase and Future Innovations</h3>\n    <p>Currently in its pilot phase, Khanmigo AI is actively gathering insights from testers. Users can anticipate the rollout of new features, each announcement delivered directly through email and social media channels. This transparent communication ensures that users stay informed and engaged as the tool evolves.</p>\n</div>', 'Students can use Khanmigo for personalized tutoring in various subjects including computer science.\nTeachers can use Khanmigo for insights on student progress and areas of improvement.\nDonors can support the development of Khanmigo and other online education resources.', 'https://www.khanacademy.org/khan-labs?via=studentaitools', NULL, 'https://cdn.kastatic.org/images/apple-touch-icon-144x144-precomposed.new.png', 'khan-academy-khanmigo-top.png', 'khan-academy-khanmigo-middle.png', 'khan-academy-khanmigo-bottom.png', 1, 0, 'free', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(37, 1, 'eSpark', 'espark', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Revolutionizing Elementary Education with eSpark</h3>\n    <p>eSpark emerges as a transformative AI-powered educational tool designed specifically for grades K-5. This innovative platform offers personalized instruction and practice in both math and reading, redefining how teachers, administrators, and students approach elementary education.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">A Research-Based Curriculum for Tailored Learning</h3>\n    <p>eSpark\'s strength lies in its research-based curriculum, providing a solid foundation for personalized learning experiences. The tool boasts a diverse array of interactive math and reading activities, engaging students and catering to their individual learning needs.</p>\n    <p>Utilizing AI, eSpark goes beyond conventional approaches by offering choice texts to students, allowing them to explore and learn at their own pace. The platform covers a spectrum of topics, including counting, sight words, syllables, addition, subtraction, division, multiplication, and more, making it a comprehensive educational companion.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Empowering Teachers with Comprehensive Tools</h3>\n    <p>eSpark facilitates easy integration into teaching methods by providing both guided lessons and instructional videos. Teachers gain real-time insights into student progress, with the tool identifying learning gaps. Detailed online reports and personalized email updates empower teachers to monitor growth and intervene with precision when necessary.</p>\n    <p>The tool extends its support to differentiated instruction through small group lessons and activities, ensuring that each student receives a tailored educational experience.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Administrative Insights for Continuous Improvement</h3>\n    <p>Administrators benefit from eSpark\'s robust reporting system, allowing them to track class trends and pinpoint areas of improvement. Aligned with the Every Student Succeeds Act (ESSA), eSpark provides evidence-based interventions for students requiring additional support, making it a vital tool in meeting educational standards.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Endorsements from Educators</h3>\n    <p>eSpark earns high praise from educators who witness significant gains in their students\' learning and confidence. The platform not only saves teachers time through targeted lessons and small group assignments but also offers a wealth of resources, feedback, and support for student learning.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Seamless Integration and Widening Impact</h3>\n    <p>eSpark\'s user-friendly approach extends to roster and assessment integrations, simplifying the onboarding process for teachers. With over 1 million students already benefiting from eSpark in their classrooms, its impact on elementary education is both tangible and widespread.</p>\n</div>', 'Engaging students with interactive activities.\nMonitoring student progress and identifying learning gaps.\nTracking class trends and providing evidence-based interventions.', 'https://www.esparklearning.com/?via=studentaitools', NULL, 'https://www.esparklearning.com/app/uploads/2023/06/cropped-favicon-32x32.png', 'espark-top.png', 'espark-middle.png', 'espark-bottom.png', 1, 0, 'free', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(38, 1, 'Solidly', 'solidly', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Unlocking Efficiency with Solidlyai: An AI-Powered Project Management Marvel</h3>\n    <p>Solidlyai emerges as a revolutionary AI-powered project management tool, dedicated to helping cross-functional teams reclaim their time and enhance collaboration. This innovative tool is designed to streamline communication, reduce distractions, and ultimately foster a more productive work environment.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Communication Assistant: Taming the Distraction Beast</h3>\n    <p>At the core of Solidlyai\'s prowess is its communication assistant, a game-changing feature that addresses the incessant pings and distractions that often hinder team productivity. By curbing these interruptions, Solidlyai ensures that teams can stay focused on their tasks without being pulled away by constant messages.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Instant Access to Critical Context: Redefining Collaboration</h3>\n    <p>Solidlyai provides instant access to critical context, a crucial element in efficient collaboration. This instant access translates to fewer meetings and less time spent responding to messages. The tool empowers teams to make informed decisions without the need for extensive back-and-forth communication.</p>\n    <p>The ability to listen to messages and convert notifications into summaries is a standout feature of Solidlyai. Team members can quickly catch up on work without the need to sift through lengthy messages, leading to a significant boost in productivity.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Custom Briefs and Intelligent Updates: Tailoring Communication</h3>\n    <p>Solidlyai takes communication to the next level by prompting team members for updates and sending custom briefs to partner teams. This personalized approach ensures that everyone is on the same page, reducing the chances of miscommunication and fostering a collaborative work environment.</p>\n    <p>The tool\'s ability to summarize messages further contributes to time savings. Team members no longer need to spend excessive time sifting through emails and Slack messages, allowing them to focus on high-impact tasks.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Focused Teams, Saved Hours: The Solidlyai Advantage</h3>\n    <p>Solidlyai empowers teams to focus on what truly matters, leading to the saving of valuable hours each day. By providing a consolidated and streamlined platform for communication and project management, Solidlyai stands as a catalyst for enhanced productivity and collaboration in cross-functional teams.</p>\n</div>', 'Saves time by reducing nonstop pings and distractions between teams within an organization.\nProvides instant access to critical context for project documents and emails..\nReduces time spent sifting through emails and slacks for teams..\nPrompts team members for updates on on-going projects.\nSends custom briefs to partner teams on running projects and open topics..', 'https://solidly-ai.webflow.io/?via=studentaitools', NULL, 'https://assets-global.website-files.com/648db778bdcb444587995259/64905308d3731fb704eef861_Solidly%20logo_256%20256%20pixel.png', 'solidly-top.png', 'solidly-middle.png', 'solidly-bottom.png', 1, 0, 'free', NULL, NULL, NULL),
