(41, 1, 'Caktus AI', 'caktus-ai', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Unveiling Caktus.ai: Transformative AI in Education</h3>\n    <p>Caktus.ai emerges as a revolutionary educational AI tool, dedicated to enhancing the learning experience for students and learners. Offering a diverse range of services, it serves as a multifaceted solution to various academic challenges.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Diverse Services Tailored for Academic Excellence</h3>\n    <p>Caktus.ai caters to an array of use cases, leveraging AI for tasks such as essay writing, mathematics problem-solving, and language learning. This comprehensive approach aims to address the varied needs of students, providing them with valuable tools to excel in their academic pursuits.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">A Gateway to Improved Academic Performance</h3>\n    <p>At its core, Caktus.ai is designed to be a catalyst for academic improvement. By offering accurate and relevant information across a broad spectrum of topics and subjects, it becomes an indispensable companion for students seeking to elevate their academic performance.</p>\n    <p>But Caktus.ai doesn\'t stop there. It goes beyond traditional academic support by providing alternative features like content creation. Students can leverage the tool to generate meta descriptions for blog posts and other content, expanding its utility beyond the confines of a typical educational tool.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Empowering Creativity with Caktus.ai</h3>\n    <p>One of the standout features of Caktus.ai is its ability to foster creativity. Through content creation capabilities, students can venture into the realm of crafting compelling meta descriptions. This additional dimension adds a layer of versatility to the tool, making it a holistic resource for academic and creative endeavors.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Embracing Comprehensive Academic Support</h3>\n    <p>In essence, Caktus.ai emerges as more than just an educational tool; it\'s a comprehensive support system. By combining AI-driven academic assistance with creative content creation features, it becomes a dynamic force in the quest for better academic outcomes.</p>\n</div>', 'Automating homework assignments.\nCreating personalized study plans.\nGenerating quizzes and tests.', 'https://www.caktus.ai/?via=studentaitools', NULL, 'https://d1muf25xaso8hp.cloudfront.net/https%3A%2F%2Fe2c066d76c1f8df738d1acebc86e1802.cdn.bubble.io%2Fd147%2Ff1695747603409x559375021375688260%2FFavicon-64.png?w=128&h=&auto=compress&dpr=1&fit=max', 'caktus-ai-top.png', 'caktus-ai-middle.png', 'caktus-ai-bottom.png', 1, 0, 'free', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(42, 1, 'Shiken', 'shiken', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Unveiling Shiken AI Tool: Revolutionizing Learning</h3>\n    <p>Shiken, an advanced learning app, goes beyond conventional learning methods to elevate your educational experience. This all-in-one app is meticulously crafted to make learning not just efficient but also enjoyable. With its innovative AI-assisted features, Shiken propels your learning speed, enabling you to achieve higher grades in less time.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">The Essence of Shiken\'s Learning Journey</h3>\n    <p>Shiken\'s arsenal of features is designed to cater to every aspect of your learning journey. From live quizzes and courses to interactive flashcards and mindfulness exercises, Shiken transforms the way you learn, making it more effective and engaging.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Key Features Redefining Learning Excellence</h3>\n    <ul>\n        <li>**Live Quizzes and Courses:** Immerse yourself in live quizzes and courses, fostering real-time interaction and dynamic learning experiences.</li>\n        <li>**Flashcards:** Reinforce your learning with interactive flashcards, a proven method to enhance memory retention.</li>\n        <li>**Mindfulness Exercises:** Balance your learning journey with mindfulness exercises, promoting mental well-being and focus.</li>\n        <li>**Notes and Game-based Learning:** Utilize Shiken\'s innovative approach to note-taking and game-based learning to make studying more enjoyable and effective.</li>\n        <li>**Study Buddies and Leaderboards:** Connect with study buddies and explore friendly competition through leaderboards, creating a collaborative and motivating learning environment.</li>\n        <li>**Customizable Learning Sessions:** Tailor your learning experience with customizable