(43, 1, 'Jobs Scout', 'jobs-scout', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Revolutionizing Job Searches with Jobs-Scout</h3>\n    <p>Jobs-Scout, an innovative AI-based job search tool, redefines the job-hunting landscape by providing unparalleled insights and analysis of job posts and resumes. This tool is designed to empower users, helping them navigate the competitive job market and accelerate their journey towards securing their dream job.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">The Power of AI in Job Hunting</h3>\n    <p>Jobs-Scout stands out as an AI-driven solution that goes beyond traditional job search tools. By analyzing job posts and resumes, it offers invaluable insights to users, highlighting crucial elements and providing a strategic advantage in the job-seeking process.</p>\n    <p>This tool brings efficiency and organization to the job search process. Users can effortlessly track job interests and, remarkably, generate sample cover letters tailored to their actual experience, streamlining the application process.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Key Features of Jobs-Scout</h3>\n    <ul>\n        <li>**Insightful Analysis:** Jobs-Scout\'s AI performs in-depth analysis of job posts and resumes, offering users a comprehensive understanding of the job market.</li>\n        <li>**Strategic Guidance:** Identify missing elements in resumes and job applications, receiving targeted suggestions to enhance competitiveness.</li>\n        <li>**Organized Job Tracking:** Effortlessly track job interests within the platform, streamlining the job search process.</li>\n        <li>**Automated Cover Letter Generation:** Generate sample cover letters based on actual experience, saving time and ensuring a professional application.</li>\n    </ul>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Simplified Job Search Experience</h3>\n    <p>Jobs-Scout is engineered to simplify the job search experience. Its intuitive interface and AI-driven features transform the daunting task of job hunting into a well-guided and strategic process.</p>\n    <p>Users can leverage the power of Jobs-Scout to gain a competitive edge in their job search. By understanding the intricacies of job posts and receiving personalized recommendations, they position themselves as strong contenders in the job market.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Empowering Users with AI Assistance</h3>\n    <p>Jobs-Scout\'s AI-driven approach is not just about analysis; it\'s about empowerment. The tool becomes a reliable companion, providing users with the tools they need to succeed in their job search journey.</p>\n    <p>Generating sample cover letters based on actual experience is a testament to Jobs-Scout\'s commitment to practical assistance. It\'s not just about finding jobs; it\'s about guiding users towards presenting their best selves to potential employers.</p>\n</div>', 'Analyze job posts and resumes.\nTrack job interests.\nGenerate sample cover letters.', 'https://jobs-scout.com/?via=studentaitools', NULL, 'https://jobs-scout.com/favicon.ico', 'jobs-scout-top.png', 'jobs-scout-middle.png', 'jobs-scout-bottom.png', 1, 0, 'free', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(44, 1, 'To Teach', 'to-teach', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Empowering Educators: AI-Driven Personalization in Teaching Materials</h3>\n    <p>The AI tool designed for teachers stands as a beacon of personalized education, offering tailor-made teaching materials and exercises that cater to the unique needs and interests of each student. This transformative tool redefines the teaching landscape, providing both free and paid plans to suit educators at various levels.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Diverse Plans for Varied Educational Needs</h3>\n    <p>Teachers leveraging this AI system gain access to a spectrum of plans, each offering distinct advantages in exercise, worksheet, and lesson plan creation. The flexibility of these plans ensures that educators can align the tool with their teaching objectives, creating a truly customized teaching experience.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Harmony of AI and Human Teaching</h3>\n    <p>This AI system is not a replacement for human teachers but a powerful ally. It operates on a human-centered approach, enhancing the capabilities of educators rather than overshadowing them. The synergy between AI and human teaching fosters an environment where technology complements the art of teaching.</p>\n    <p>Within this extract, the focus is on the essence of the AI system\'s collaboration with human teachers. The absence of pricing information and marketing fluff underscores a commitment to providing genuine insights into the tool\'s functionality and benefits.</p>\n</div>', 'Create customized lesson plans.\nGenerate tailored exercises for students.\nEnhance human teaching abilities with AI support.', 'https://to-teach.ai/?via=studentaitools', NULL, 'https://www.to-teach.ai/build/_assets/favicon-SXJVSDO4.png', 'to-teach-top.png', 'to-teach-middle.png', 'to-teach-bottom.png', 1, 0, 'free', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(45, 1, 'Learnt.ai', 'learnt.ai', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Decoding Learnt.ai: Transforming Education with AI</h3>\n    <p>Learnt.ai emerges as a groundbreaking AI tool tailored for education professionals. Its unique approach involves harnessing the power of artificial intelligence to automate the creation of diverse educational content, ranging from lesson plans to assessment questions.</p>\n    <p>This innovative tool doesn\'t seek to replace educators but rather empowers them to elevate their craft. By automating certain tasks, Learnt.ai frees up valuable time for educators to focus on what they do best—inspiring and engaging with students.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">AI-Powered Tools at Your Fingertips</h3>\n    <p>Learnt.ai boasts a robust repertoire of over 65 tools and AI sidekicks. Each tool is crafted to simplify the lives of educators, offering a range of functionalities to enhance the teaching and learning experience.</p>\n    <p>Whether it\'s crafting compelling lesson plans, designing creative homework tasks, incorporating icebreakers for class engagement, or formulating effective assessment questions, Learnt.ai has educators covered.</p>\n    <p>What sets Learnt.ai apart is its commitment to quality. The AI algorithms not only automate tasks but do so while maintaining the highest standards of content creation, ensuring that the educational materials generated are not just convenient but also of exceptional quality.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Balancing Automation with Creativity</h3>\n    <p>Learnt.ai operates on the principle of augmentation, not replacement. The goal is to enhance the creative capacities of educators, encouraging them to delve into the art of teaching while leaving repetitive tasks to the AI sidekicks.</p>\n    <p>By automating