(48, 1, 'Monic.ai', 'monic.ai', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Monic.ai: Redefining Learning with AI-Powered Innovation</h3>\n    <p>Monic.ai emerges as a groundbreaking AI-powered learning tool, dedicated to transforming your learning journey into an interactive, effective, and enjoyable experience. Supporting over 60 languages, Monic.ai becomes your ultimate learning copilot, assisting you in creating assessments, flashcards, summaries, and study guides in mere seconds.</p>\n    <p>How does Monic.ai achieve this? The answer lies in its innovative use of artificial intelligence (AI) models. By analyzing and processing your uploaded materials, whether they are files, text, YouTube video links, or documents, Monic.ai leverages AI to generate customized resources tailored to your learning needs.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">The Power of Monic.ai\'s Advanced AI</h3>\n    <p>Monic.ai\'s advanced AI takes the heavy lifting out of learning. Rapidly analyzing materials, it generates a diverse set of resources aimed at enhancing your learning experience. From smart study tools like spaced repetition to simulated exams, Monic.ai offers a comprehensive library of learning techniques that ensure information retention.</p>\n    <p>Testimonials from thousands of learners attest to the efficacy of Monic.ai. Users have praised its incredible discovery features and how it significantly improves study content. The automated flashcard system, in particular, has received acclaim for its impressive comprehension level. With Monic.ai, learning transcends the ordinary, becoming interactive, effective, and enjoyable for all.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Monic.ai: Empowering Professionals and Avid Learners Alike</h3>\n    <p>Monic.ai isn\'t confined to the realm of students; professionals can 