(49, 1, 'Education CoPilot', 'education-copilot', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Unlocking Efficiency with AI Lesson Planner</h3>\n    <p>AI Lesson Planner emerges as a revolutionary AI tool in the realm of education, simplifying the intricate process of lesson plan preparation. With its intuitive features, it goes beyond mere automation, generating templates for lesson plans, prompts, educational handouts, student reports, and project outlines.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">A Multifaceted Toolbox for Educators</h3>\n    <p>AI Lesson Planner doesn\'t stop at lesson plans. It unfolds as a comprehensive toolbox, offering more than 10 tools designed to save educators valuable time outside the classroom. The tool\'s versatility shines as it caters to users in both English and Spanish, breaking language barriers for a more inclusive educational experience.</p>\n    <p>The primary goal is clear — to deliver high-quality, structured lesson plans and resources that alleviate the burden on educators, allowing them to focus more on their students and less on administrative tasks.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">The Rich Palette of AI Lesson Planner</h3>\n    <ul>\n        <li>**Lesson Plan Templates:** Instantly generate professional and structured lesson plans that meet the highest educational standards.</li>\n        <li>**Prompts and Handouts:** Elevate classroom engagement with carefully crafted prompts and educational handouts that supplement your lessons.</li>\n        <li>**Student Reports:** Streamline the reporting process with AI Lesson Planner\'s tools for generating insightful student reports.</li>\n        <li>**Project Outlines:** Facilitate project-based learning with detailed project outlines that guide students through meaningful tasks.</li>\n    </ul>\n</div>\n\n<di