(50, 1, 'Xtool AI TTS', 'xtool-ai-tts', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Revolutionizing Content Creation with AI-Generated Articles and Text-to-Speech Conversion</h3>\n    <p>Embark on a transformative journey with AI-App, your go-to platform for AI-generated articles and seamless text-to-speech conversion. This innovative tool redefines the way content is created and delivered, offering a host of features to meet diverse needs.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Effortless Content Generation</h3>\n    <p>Say goodbye to the days of struggling to create compelling content. With AI-App, generating articles is as simple as inputting your title. The AI engine takes care of the rest, producing content that you can edit and refine to perfection.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Voice Customization Made Easy</h3>\n    <p>AI-App goes beyond text by offering a powerful text-to-speech (TTS) feature. Choose from a variety of voice roles, accents, and tones to give your content a unique and engaging flair. Adjust voice speed and volume settings to match your preferences seamlessly.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Instant Audio Results</h3>\n    <p>Transform your written content into immersive audio experiences with just one click. AI-App enables you to generate voice results and convert text to MP3 files effortlessly. This feature is a game-changer for those looking to enhance accessibility or repurpose text-based content.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Diverse Voice Options</h3>\n    <p>Explore a range of voice options that suit your project requirements. Whether you need a professional tone, a friendly voice, or a specific accent, AI-App has you covered. This versatility ensures that your content resonates with your target audience.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Fine-Tune Your Audio Experience</h3>\n    <p>AI-App puts you in control of your audio content. Adjust voice speed and volume settings to create an auditory experience that aligns with your vision. This level of customization ensures that your content is not only engaging but also perfectly tailored to your audience.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Versatility for Every Need</h3>\n    <p>Whether you\'re looking to generate articles with AI assistance or convert text to speech for enhanced accessibility, AI-App is your all-in-one solution. Its versatile features cater to a range of content creation needs, making it an indispensable tool in your arsenal.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Unlock the Power of AI in Content Generation</h3>\n    <p>Experience the transformative power of AI in content creation and text-to-speech conversion. AI-App empowers you to repurpose text-based content effortlessly, opening new possibilities in accessibility and engagement. Embrace the future of content creation with AI-App.</p>\n</div>', 'Automated article writing on any topic, given the title.\nCreating audio content from articles and text content.\nEnhancing accessibility of written content with audio versions.', 'https://tts.xtool.ai?via=studentaitools', NULL, 'https://tts.xtool.ai/favicon.ico', 'xtool-ai-tts-top.png', 'xtool-ai-tts-middle.png', 'xtool-ai-tts-bottom.png', 1, 0, 'free', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(51, 1, 'AI Checker Tool', 'ai-checker-tool', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Unveiling the AI Checker Tool: Your Comprehensive AI Content Detector</h3>\n    <p>The AI Checker Tool emerges as a cutting-edge, free, and precise AI content detector tool. Employing advanced algorithms, it excels in accurately discerning whether a text is the creation of AI models such as GPT-3, GPT-4, BARD, and OpenAI.</p>\n    <p>Designed to cater to a diverse audience, this tool proves invaluable for writers, students, educators, content marketers, freelancers, editors, publishers, researchers, and content consumers. It provides a nuanced analysis of text, revealing the origin—whether it\'s crafted by a human or generated by AI, or even a harmonious blend of both.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Precision at Its Core</h3>\n    <p>The AI Checker Tool boasts an impressive 98% accuracy rate, effectively minimizing error rates to less than 1%. This exceptional accuracy ensures reliable results, making it a go-to tool for users seeking precision in their content analysis.</p>\n    <p>Furthermore, its multilingual support enhances versatility, catering to users across different language backgrounds and content types. Whether you\'re dealing with English, Spanish, French, or any other language, the AI Checker Tool stands ready to serve.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Unleashing Advanced Capabilities</h3>\n    <p>This tool goes beyond mere content analysis. It aids users in identifying potential plagiarism and pinpointing possible sources, eliminating the need for tedious manual checks. The AI Checker Tool transforms the way content authenticity is verified, offering a seamless and efficient solution.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Important Note: Purpose and Limitations</h3>\n    <p>It\'s crucial to recognize that the AI Checker Tool is designed exclusively for analysis and detection purposes. It is not intended for publishing or sharing plagiarized content. Users are encouraged to utilize the tool responsibly, respecting ethical considerations and the integrity of content creation.</p>\n</div>', 'Detecting AI-generated content.\nIdentifying text sources if it was generated by AI.\nChecking for potential plagiarism in a piece of text.\nVerifying content authenticity.', 'https://aicheckertool.com/?via=studentaitools', NULL, NULL, 'ai-checker-tool-top.png', 'ai-checker-tool-middle.png', 'ai-checker-tool-bottom.png', 1, 0, 'free', NULL, NULL, NULL);
