(56, 1, 'TutorAI', 'tutorai', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Discovering TutorAI: A Gateway to Versatile Learning</h3>\n    <p>TutorAI stands as an online educational powerhouse, enabling users to delve into a vast array of subjects, from the intricacies of physics to the depths of American history — and yes, even exploring the nuances of one\'s own name! This platform reimagines education, offering a rich tapestry of learning materials, interactive quizzes, and personalized learning experiences.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Educational Abundance at Your Fingertips</h3>\n    <p>TutorAI is more than just an online platform; it\'s a repository of knowledge. Users can access a diverse range of educational materials, including comprehensive notes, engaging tutorials, and interactive quizzes that make learning an immersive and enjoyable experience.</p>\n    <p>The platform\'s commitment to variety ensures that learners can find resources tailored to their specific interests and educational needs. Whether diving into the complexities of academic subjects or embarking on a self-discovery journey, TutorAI provides the tools needed for a well-rounded education.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Personalized Learning, Empowered Users</h3>\n    <p>One of TutorAI\'s standout features is its emphasis on personalized learning. Users have the freedom to tailor their learning experiences, creating a curriculum that suits their individual preferences and goals. This personalized approach extends to tracking progress, ensuring that learners can measure their advancement and celebrate milestones.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">The TutorAI Learning Experience</h3>\n    <ul>\n        <li>**Educational Materials:** Access a wealth of educational materials, from in-depth notes to interactive tutorials, providing a comprehensive learning experience.</li>\n        <li>**Interactive Quizzes:** Reinforce learning through interactive quizzes that engage and challenge users, making the learning journey dynamic and effective.</li>\n        <li>**Customization:** Tailor your learning path with TutorAI\'s customization features, ensuring that your educational journey aligns with your unique interests and goals.</li>\n        <li>**Progress Tracking:** Stay informed about your academic journey with built-in progress tracking, turning learning into a measurable and rewarding experience.</li>\n    </ul>\n</div>', 'Learn physics and American history.\nCustomize learning experience.\nTrack progress and improve skills.', 'https://tutorai.me/?via=studentaitools', NULL, 'https://www.tutorai.me/owl_emoji.ico', 'tutorai-top.png', 'tutorai-middle.png', 'tutorai-bottom.png', 1, 0, 'free', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(57, 1, 'Tutorly', 'tutorly', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Unlocking Academic Excellence with Tutorly.ai</h3>\n    <p>Embark on a revolutionary learning journey with Tutorly.ai, an AI-powered homework help tool that redefines how students approach their academic challenges. With a chat-based interface, Tutorly.ai becomes a personalized guide, offering assistance in various academic endeavors.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Seamless Access and User-Friendly Interface</h3>\n    <p>Tutorly.ai prioritizes accessibility, allowing users to login or register for free. The tool\'s functionality is enhanced by enabling javascript, ensuring a smooth and responsive user experience. By attaching a string of text and using the code \"welcome\" within a valid month, users unlock the full potential of Tutorly.ai.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Versatile Support for Academic Queries</h3>\n    <p>One of Tutorly.ai\'s standout features is its ability to cater to diverse academic needs. Users can pose questions, seek assistance with essays, and leverage the tool\'s paraphrasing capabilities. This versatility positions Tutorly.ai as a comprehensive solution for various academic challenges.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Premium Services for Enhanced Learning</h3>\n    <p>For users seeking an elevated experience, Tutorly.ai offers additional services through account upgrades. This opens the door to a realm of advanced features, providing an enriched learning environment for those committed to academic excellence.</p>\n</div>', 'Ask homework questions.\nGet help with essays.\nParaphrasing assistance.', 'https://tutorly.ai/?via=studentaitools', NULL, 'https://tutorly.ai/icon.ico?00c96ba816287d0d', 'tutorly-top.png', 'tutorly-middle.png', 'tutorly-bottom.png', 1, 0, 'free', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(58, 1, 'Isaac Editor', 'isaac-editor', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Decoding Excellence: The Isaac Editor</h3>\n    <p>The Isaac Editor emerges as a groundbreaking AI-powered text editor meticulously crafted for the realm of academic writing. With a mission to enhance the writing experience, this tool has garnered acclaim, drawing in a community of over 12,000 students and researchers seeking a more efficient and satisfying writing journey.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Crafting Efficiency with Isaac</h3>\n    <p>At its core, The Isaac Editor offers a menu-driven interface that empowers users to delve into their writing projects with unparalleled efficiency. This intuitive tool is tailored to meet the unique demands of academic writing, ensuring a seamless and productive writing experience.</p>\n</div>', 'Efficient academic writing.\nImproved writing experience.\nAI-powered text editing.', 'https://isaaceditor.com/?via=studentaitools', NULL, NULL, 'isaac-editor-top.png', 'isaac-editor-middle.png', 'isaac-editor-bottom.png', 1, 0, 'free', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(59, 1, 'Teachermatic', 'teachermatic', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Teachermatic: Transforming Education with AI-Powered Teaching</h3>\n    <p>Teachermatic stands as a groundbreaking AI-powered platform meticulously crafted for educators, aiming to revolutionize the art of teaching. Built on the formidable GPT-3 technology, this platform redefines the role of educators by alleviating their workload and allowing them to prioritize what truly matters: the students.</p>\n    <p>Whether you\'re a seasoned veteran or a novice in the teaching profession, Teachermatic becomes your ally, making the job easier and more efficient through the remarkable power of AI.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">AI-Powered Lesson Planning for Educators</h3>\n    <p>Teachermatic revolutionizes lesson planning by serving as a personal AI-planning assistant for educators. It goes beyond the mundane and provides a starting point and framework for teachers across all subjects. This approach encourages educators to channel their energies into creating more engaging and creative classes, enriching the learning experience for students.</p>\n    <p>The platform boasts AI generators that simplify the creation of high-quality classroom resources, including lesson plans, activities, worksheets, and more. Leveraging advanced language processing algorithms, these generators comprehend the teacher\'s input and generate materials tailored to their desired topic.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Empowering Educators with AI-Driven Tools</h3>\n    <p>Teachermatic goes beyond lesson planning and offers an array of AI-driven tools designed to enhance the daily tasks of teachers. These include:</p>\n    <ul>\n        <li>**Multiple-Choice Quiz Maker:** Streamline quiz creation with an AI-powered tool that generates multiple-choice quizzes effortlessly.</li>\n        <li>**Scheme Work Generator:** Simplify the creation of schemes of work, saving teachers valuable time in curriculum planning.</li>\n        <li>**Class Question Generator:** Engage students with thought-provoking questions generated by AI, fostering a dynamic classroom environment.</li>\n        <li>**Rubric Generator:** Automate the creation of rubrics for assessments, ensuring consistency and fairness in grading.</li>\n        <li>**Glossary Generator:** Build comprehensive glossaries with AI assistance, enriching classroom resources.</li>\n    </ul>\n    <p>These tools are more than features; they are a testament to Teachermatic\'s commitment to supporting educators by automating tedious tasks and providing valuable resources.</p>\n</div>', 'Save time on lesson planning.\nCreate high-quality resources.\nGenerate quizzes and rubrics.\nAutomate teaching tasks.\nImprove staff wellbeing.', 'https://teachermatic.com/?via=studentaitools', NULL, 'https://i0.wp.com/teachermatic.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/cropped-color.png?fit=32%2C32&ssl=1', 'teachermatic-top.png', 'teachermatic-middle.png', 'teachermatic-bottom.png', 1, 0, 'free', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(60, 1, 'Slatebox', 'slatebox', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Unlocking Creativity with Slatebox: A Dive into AI-Powered Visualizations</h3>\n    <p>Slatebox, an ingenious AI tool, revolutionizes the creation of editable visualizations through natural language prompts and mind-maps. This versatile tool, equipped with an auto-populate feature, simplifies the generation of diagrams and visuals, offering over 100 templates to cater to various needs.</p>\n    <p>Whether you\'re conducting a SWOT analysis or a pro-con evaluation, Slatebox has you covered. By providing a URL or a text prompt, the AI assistant swiftly generates sticky notes and populates your visualizations with precision.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Real-Time Collaboration and Seamless Integration</h3>\n    <p>Beyond its powerful AI capabilities, Slatebox introduces real-time collaboration features. Collaborate with your team on multi-cursor canvases, integrating with platforms like Microsoft Teams, Slack, and GitHub to enhance workflow efficiency. Slatebox also offers magic links for instant sharing of visualizations with team members.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Effortless Mind-Map Creation and AI-Driven Assistance</h3>\n    <p>Slatebox empowers users to build mind-maps and conduct brainstorming sessions with ease. Its intuitive interface simplifies the process — just click, change, and repeat. With AI assistance, unlock your team\'s potential in tasks like retrospectives, daily standups, and design sessions.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Privacy Controls and Seamless Collaboration</h3>\n    <p>Privacy takes center stage in Slatebox\'s design, offering Google Docs-like privacy controls for your slates. Add comments and resolve outstanding items asynchronously, fostering improved collaboration and productivity.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Templates, Themes, and Customization</h3>\n    <p>Explore Slatebox\'s extensive library of templates and themes to quickly transform the look and feel of your visualizations. Smart color picking allows easy customization of your color palette. Capture snapshots of your slates and revert to previous versions effortlessly.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Efficient App Wireframing and Concept Iteration</h3>\n    <p>Slatebox facilitates app wireframing and idea iteration through its drag-and-drop functionality. Expressive mind-maps and AI superpowers make it a standout tool for brainstorming and concept visualization. Users commend Slatebox for its simplicity and unrivaled features in the realm of concept drawing tools.</p>\n</div>', 'Visualize the make SWOT analysis.\nImprove brainstorming sessions with visual mind maps.', 'https://slatebox.com/?via=studentaitools', NULL, 'https://files.slatebox.com/slatebox_small_favicon.png', 'slatebox-top.png', 'slatebox-middle.png', 'slatebox-bottom.png', 1, 0, 'free', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(61, 1, 'Quiz Makito', 'quiz-makito', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Unveiling Quiz Makito: The Future of AI-Powered Quizzing</h3>\n    <p>Quiz Makito emerges as a groundbreaking AI-powered quiz platform, revolutionizing the way quizzes are created and experienced. Packed with features like gamified quizzes, speed-optimized creation, and regular updates, it sets a new standard for interactive and engaging learning experiences.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Features that Redefine Quiz Creation</h3>\n    <ul>\n        <li>**Gamified Quizzes:** Elevate the quiz-taking experience with gamified elements, making learning not just informative but also enjoyable.</li>\n        <li>**Speed-Optimized Creation:** Quiz creation is no longer a time-consuming task. Quiz Makito streamlines the process, allowing educators to focus on content rather than logistics.</li>\n        <li>**Regular Updates:** Stay current with the latest information and trends. Quiz Makito ensures that quizzes are always fresh and relevant with regular updates.</li>\n    </ul>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">User Engagement at Its Core</h3>\n    <p>Quiz Makito goes beyond conventional quiz platforms by providing high-quality design and detailed tracking tools. These tools not only enhance the visual appeal of quizzes but also offer valuable insights into user engagement, enabling educators to refine and optimize their content.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Interactive Learning with Quiz Builder</h3>\n    <p>Powered by OpenAI technology, Quiz Makito introduces an intuitive Quiz Builder that facilitates an interactive learning experience across diverse topics. Educators can create quizzes that captivate and challenge learners, fostering a deeper understanding of the subject matter.</p>\n</div>', 'Create engaging quizzes effortlessly with gamification and customization for effective learning..\nUtilize AI-generated quizzes for personalized learning experiences across diverse topics..\nMonitor and analyze quiz performance with detailed insights and analytics for educational improvement..', 'https://quizmakito.com/?via=studentaitools', NULL, 'https://quizmakito.com/favicon.ico', 'quiz-makito-top.png', 'quiz-makito-middle.png', 'quiz-makito-bottom.png', 1, 0, 'free', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(62, 1, 'Cliptutor', 'cliptutor', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Unlocking Educational Frontiers with ClipTutor</h3>\n    <p>ClipTutor stands as a transformative force in the realm of education, reshaping how individuals learn and teach through innovative features. This platform seamlessly converts YouTube videos into personalized tutors, harnessing the power of AI to revolutionize the learning experience.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Versatility Redefined: AI Youtube Video Chat and Beyond</h3>\n    <p>ClipTutor\'s capabilities extend far beyond a conventional learning platform. With AI Youtube video chat, users can engage in interactive sessions, fostering a dynamic and personalized learning environment. The platform\'s adaptability is further highlighted by custom quizzes, multi-language support, and media uploads.</p>\n    <p>Integration with Quizlet and Kahoot adds a competitive edge to learning. Users can seamlessly merge interactive quizzes with these platforms, creating a rich and engaging learning experience that transcends traditional boundaries.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Empowering Educators with Content Creation</h3>\n    <p>For educators, ClipTutor is a game-changer in content creation. The platform allows the transformation of video content into quizzes and flashcards, aligning with individual learning styles. This feature streamlines the process of creating personalized, effective learning materials.</p>\n    <p>ClipTutor\'s support for multiple languages makes it an inclusive tool, breaking down language barriers and making education accessible to learners worldwide.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Expanding Learning Horizons: Media Uploads and Integration</h3>\n    <p>ClipTutor empowers users to broaden their learning resources by facilitating the upload of MP3 and MP4 files. This feature adds a layer of customization, allowing users to tailor their learning experience to their unique preferences and requirements.</p>\n    <p>Integration with Quizlet and Kahoot takes learning to new heights. Users not only benefit from interactive quizzes but also gain access to extensive study resources, creating a comprehensive learning ecosystem.</p>\n</div>', 'Enhancing learning and teaching from YouTube videos.\nCreating personalized quizzes and flashcards automatically from YouTube videos.\nEngaging with fellow learners while watching videos on YouTube.', 'https://www.cliptutor.com/?via=studentaitools', NULL, 'https://www.cliptutor.com/img/icons/logo-black.png', 'cliptutor-top.png', 'cliptutor-middle.png', 'cliptutor-bottom.png', 1, 0, 'free', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(63, 1, 'BookAI.chat', 'bookai.chat', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Exploring BookAI Chat: A Revolution in Literary Interaction</h3>\n    <p>BookAI Chat, an innovative AI-powered tool, redefines the way readers engage with their favorite books. This platform simplifies the interaction process, requiring users to provide only the book\'s title and author\'s name, while the power of Artificial Intelligence takes care of the rest.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">The Multilingual Magic of BookAI Chat</h3>\n    <p>BookAI Chat breaks language barriers by supporting over 30 languages. Users can seamlessly converse with books in their native language or the language they are learning, enhancing the reading experience and accessibility for a global audience.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Effortless Library Management</h3>\n    <p>This AI-powered tool goes beyond simple interaction; it streamlines the process of managing your book library. Adding new books is a breeze, requiring minimal input from users. Additionally, the platform allows users to include a cover image, adding a visual touch to their virtual bookshelf.</p>\n</div>', 'Effortless book cataloging and management.\nLanguage learning through native book conversations.\nQuick and accurate book information retrieval.', 'https://www.bookai.chat/?via=studentaitools', NULL, NULL, 'bookai.chat-top.png', 'bookai.chat-middle.png', 'bookai.chat-bottom.png', 1, 0, 'free', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(64, 1, 'MAGMA Tutor', 'magma-tutor', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Unlocking the Potential of AI with Magma</h3>\n    <p>Magma stands as a beacon of innovation in the realm of AI tutors, dedicated to helping learners achieve their goals. Through its intelligent personalization, Magma tailors the learning experience to meet the unique needs and abilities of each user, fostering a journey towards mastery.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Revolutionizing Learning with AI Microlearning</h3>\n    <p>At the heart of Magma is its groundbreaking AI-powered microlearning approach. This innovative strategy shapes personalized learning paths, allowing users to monitor and celebrate their progress as they strive for mastery in various subjects.</p>\n    <p>Whether you\'re a student navigating academic challenges or a lifelong learner pursuing knowledge, Magma is your dedicated companion in the quest for learning excellence.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Browser Support for Seamless Learning</h3>\n    <p>Magma brings the convenience of browser support to the forefront, ensuring that users can access a wealth of valuable information with ease. The user-friendly interface enhances the learning experience, making knowledge acquisition a seamless and enjoyable process.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Embark on Your Learning Journey with Magma</h3>\n    <p>Experience the transformative power of personalized learning by starting your journey with Magma today. Witness how AI can elevate your learning experience, providing insights and support tailored to your individual learning style and pace.</p>\n</div>', 'Personalized learning for students with AI tutor.\nSkill development for professionals in a custom and personalized way.\nDevelop personalized self paced learning materials on any subject.', 'https://magmatutor.com/?via=studentaitools', NULL, 'https://magmatutor.com/assets/images/MagmaLogo.png', 'magma-tutor-top.png', 'magma-tutor-middle.png', 'magma-tutor-bottom.png', 1, 0, 'free', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(65, 1, 'Quizbot', 'quizbot', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Decoding Quizbot: Revolutionizing Test Question Generation</h3>\n    <p>Quizbot emerges as a groundbreaking AI tool, dedicated to the seamless creation of high-quality test questions in English. Leveraging the principles of Bloom\'s taxonomy, Quizbot ensures that generated questions align with various cognitive levels, fostering a comprehensive assessment experience.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Diverse Question Formats for Varied Assessments</h3>\n    <p>Quizbot offers a versatile array of question formats, catering to the diverse needs of educators and learners. From multiple choice and true-false to fill in the blank, short answer, and open-ended questions, the tool provides a dynamic platform for crafting assessments that truly measure understanding and knowledge.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">User-Friendly Content Input</h3>\n    <p>Users can effortlessly upload text, links, and videos to Quizbot, unlocking the potential to create questions from a variety of content sources. This flexibility enhances the tool\'s usability and accommodates different teaching and learning styles.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Tailoring Questions to Your Style</h3>\n    <p>Quizbot goes a step further by allowing users to customize question generation to match their preferred writing style. This feature ensures that assessments not only evaluate knowledge but also reflect the unique voice and approach of the instructor or content creator.</p>\n</div>', 'Create quizzes for online courses.\nGenerate practice tests for students quickly.\nAssess employee knowledge in training programs.', 'https://quizbot.ai/?via=studentaitools', NULL, NULL, 'quizbot-top.png', 'quizbot-middle.png', 'quizbot-bottom.png', 1, 0, 'free', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(66, 1, 'CourseMind', 'coursemind', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Revolutionizing Online Education with CourseMind</h3>\n    <p>CourseMind, an AI-powered marvel, redefines how you manage your online school or organization. This comprehensive tool consolidates all aspects of school administration, providing an efficient and seamless experience for both administrators and members.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Centralized School Management Made Easy</h3>\n    <p>CourseMind simplifies the process of building and managing your school. All the essential features are seamlessly integrated, offering administrators a powerful platform to oversee and streamline operations.</p>\n    <p>One of the standout features of CourseMind is its course creation capabilities. Users can create courses with detailed usage instructions and leverage a diverse set of content creation tools. This empowers educators to build engaging and interactive courses that capture the attention of their audience.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Crafting Engaging Courses with CourseMind</h3>\n    <p>The heart of CourseMind lies in its ability to facilitate the creation of captivating courses. With a plethora of content creation tools at your disposal, you can craft lessons that resonate with your audience. Detailed usage instructions ensure that educators can navigate the course creation process effortlessly.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Empowering Your Marketing Efforts</h3>\n    <p>CourseMind doesn\'t just stop at course creation; it equips you with a suite of marketing tools to amplify your reach. From email automation to the convenience of landing page builders, CourseMind provides a comprehensive toolkit for effective content promotion and