nce. Define bonuses to augment the value of your offer and captivate your audience.</p>\n</div>', 'Create and launch different types of courses faster and easier.\nPlan lesson content quickly for teachers and tutors.\nGenerate compelling content for employee training and more.', 'https://courses.ai/?via=studentaitools', NULL, 'https://d1muf25xaso8hp.cloudfront.net/https%3A%2F%2F91290abb9ad8df30994d4a31ea0c8785.cdn.bubble.io%2Ff1685033429277x886037856833372600%2Ffavicon.png?w=128&h=&auto=compress&dpr=1&fit=max', 'courses.ai-top.png', 'courses.ai-middle.png', 'courses.ai-bottom.png', 1, 0, 'free', NULL, NULL, NULL);
