(70, 1, 'Chatlingo', 'chatlingo', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Embark on Language Learning with ChatLingo</h3>\n    <p>ChatLingo stands as a beacon in the realm of language learning platforms, offering a dynamic and interactive approach to mastering new languages. Dive into the world of linguistic exploration through engaging conversations with AI friends, redefining the way languages are learned.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Revolutionizing Language Learning through Conversations</h3>\n    <p>ChatLingo introduces a novel method of language practice — real, interactive conversations with virtual mentors. These AI companions serve as guides on your language learning journey, providing a unique and immersive experience that goes beyond traditional methods.</p>\n    <p>Immerse yourself in languages such as Irish, French, German, Spanish, Portuguese, Italian, Dutch, Mandarin, and Japanese with unprecedented speed and efficiency. ChatLingo accelerates the learning process by focusing on practical conversations, allowing users to discuss topics that resonate with them rather than relying solely on textbooks.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Key Features of ChatLingo</h3>\n    <ul>\n        <li>**Real Conversations:** Engage in genuine conversations for language learning, bringing authenticity and relevance to your linguistic journey.</li>\n        <li>**Virtual Mentors:** Benefit from AI mentors who are available 24/7 to guide and assist, replicating the support of a native speaker.</li>\n        <li>**Grammar Exercises:** Hone your language skills with dedicated grammar exercises that reinforce your understanding of language structure.</li>\n    </ul>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">24/7 Support from AI Mentors</h3>\n    <p>One of ChatLingo\'s standout features is the constant availability of AI mentors. These virtual guides are ready to answer your questions and provide assistance at any time, ensuring a seamless learning experience reminiscent of interacting with a native speaker.</p>\n</div>', 'Improve language fluency through interactive conversations.\nPractice speaking skills with virtual mentors.\nLearn languages in a conversational and engaging way.', 'https://www.chatlingo.app/?via=studentaitools', NULL, 'https://www.chatlingo.app/assets/favicon-9694e0213dfde6a87a60ca8b12b9ecd21a30b77119677daa2a0d508de27c09b6.png', 'chatlingo-top.png', 'chatlingo-middle.png', 'chatlingo-bottom.png', 1, 0, 'free', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(71, 1, 'MathGPTPro', 'mathgptpro', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Unlocking Mathematical Prowess with MathGPTPro</h3>\n    <p>MathGPTPro stands as a testament to the fusion of artificial intelligence and mathematical problem-solving. The tool, powered by AI, simplifies the often daunting realm of mathematical problem-solving, making it accessible to a broad audience.</p>\n    <p>The onboarding process is seamless, with easy sign-up and login options ensuring that users swiftly tap into MathGPTPro\'s advanced capabilities. Designed for individuals grappling with intricate mathematical problems, this tool emerges as a beacon of efficiency in mathematical tasks.</p>\n    <p>MathGPTPro isn\'t limited in scope—it\'s a versatile solution catering to a spectrum of mathematical challenges. From fundamental calculations to intricate equations, the tool offers a comprehensive set of features to address various mathematical tasks.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Comprehensive Mathematical Problem-Solving</h3>\n    <p>Irrespective of your role—be it a student, researcher, or professional—MathGPTPro becomes your ally in conquering complex mathematical problems. Its advanced capabilities ensure that mathematical problem-solving becomes more than just a task; it becomes an efficient and streamlined process.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">User-Friendly Interface for All</h3>\n    <p>MathGPTPro\'s commitment to accessibility is evident in its user-friendly interface. The tool accommodates users from various backgrounds and proficiency levels, ensuring that everyone can harness the power of mathematical problem-solving.</p>\n    <p>Basic calculations or intricate mathematical conundrums, MathGPTPro rises to the occasion, providing a user-friendly platform for all your mathematical needs.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Tailored Solutions for Every User</h3>\n    <p>Whether you\'re navigating the complexities of algebraic equations or diving into statistical analysis, MathGPTPro offers tailored solutions. It adapts to your specific requirements, providing a personalized experience in the realm of mathematical problem-solving.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Empowering Every Mathematician</h3>\n    <p>MathGPTPro\'s reach extends beyond traditional educational settings. It empowers students to excel in their studies, aids researchers in their explorations, and assists professionals in their daily mathematical challenges. The tool isn\'t just about solving problems; it\'s about empowering individuals to reach new heights in their mathematical journey.</p>\n</div>', 'Students can use MathGPTPro to solve complex math problems and understand the step-by-step solutions..\nResearchers can utilize MathGPTPro to tackle mathematical equations in their studies and experiments..\nProfessionals in fields like physics, engineering, and finance can rely on MathGPTPro for specialized mathematical problem-solving..', 'https://mathgptpro.com/?via=studentaitools', NULL, 'https://mathgptpro.com/MathgptCubicLogo.svg', 'mathgptpro-top.png', 'mathgptpro-middle.png', 'mathgptpro-bottom.png', 1, 0, 'free', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(72, 1, 'Essai.Pro', 'essai.pro', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Unlocking Creativity with essai.pro: Your AI Writing Companion</h3>\n    <p>Embark on a journey of enhanced writing skills with essai.pro, an AI-powered essay paper writing and paraphrasing tool. Tailored to overcome writer\'s block, essai.pro is a revolutionary platform that transforms your writing experience.</p>\n    <p>One of the standout features of essai.pro is its ability to generate captivating topics and structured outlines, providing the inspiration needed to kickstart your writing process. Harnessing the power of AI technology, the tool produces content that is not only unique but also free from plagiarism, closely mimicking human writing.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Essential Features of essai.pro</h3>\n    <ul>\n        <li>**Topic and Table of Contents Generator:** Tackle complex writing challenges with ease using essai.pro\'s powerful generator that aids in problem-solving and organization.</li>\n        <li>**Autocorrect AI:** Elevate the quality of your text by employing the autocorrect AI feature, ensuring that your writing appears more polished, human-like, and error-free.</li>\n    </ul>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Revolutionizing Education Efficiency</h3>\n    <p>The impact of technology on education is undeniable, and essai.pro plays a pivotal role in this transformation. By providing access to up-to-date information and streamlining administrative tasks for educators, technology enhances the overall efficiency of the education system.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Versatility Redefined: essai.pro in Academic Writing</h3>\n    <p>Essai.pro is not just a writing tool; it\'s a versatile companion for academic writing. Rewrite, expand, and adjust your papers to match different writing styles and tones effortlessly. The tool\'s ability to generate academic references and relevant sources adds tremendous value to your writing process.</p>\n    <p>With essai.pro, academic writing becomes a seamless and efficient endeavor, empowering writers to produce high-quality content with ease.</p>\n</div>', 'Transforming education by improving accessibility, engagement, and efficiency.\nEnhancing writing skills and generating interesting topics and outlines.\nProviding error-free text with autocorrect AI.', 'https://essai.pro/?via=studentaitools', NULL, 'https://essai.pro/favicon.ico', 'essai.pro-top.png', 'essai.pro-middle.png', 'essai.pro-bottom.png', 1, 0, 'free', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(73, 1, 'eggheads - AI-powered microlearning', 'eggheads---ai-powered-microlearning', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Empowering Businesses with Eggheads: Revolutionizing Microlearning with AI</h3>\n    <p>Eggheads stands as a pioneering AI-driven microlearning platform, revolutionizing how businesses cultivate and retain knowledge. This innovative tool is designed to ensure that information not only sticks but becomes a driving force in raising awareness across diverse industries.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Unveiling the Power of Eggheads</h3>\n    <p>Eggheads introduces a novel approach to microlearning, where customers can create, share, and analyze chat-based learning nuggets. These e-learning chatbots are easily accessible via a link or through a dedicated Microsoft Teams App aptly named the egghead.</p>\n    <p>Businesses, including insurers and banks, leverage Eggheads for various crucial functions. From onboarding new team members to reinforcing key messages, conducting product knowledge training, customer service training, to compliance training, Eggheads proves to be a versatile and indispensable asset.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Key Applications of Eggheads</h3>\n    <ul>\n        <li>**Onboarding Excellence:** Eggheads facilitates seamless onboarding processes, ensuring that new team members are efficiently brought up to speed with organizational dynamics.</li>\n        <li>**Message Reinforcement:** Businesses utilize Eggheads to reinforce key messages, fostering a unified understanding and commitment to organizational goals.</li>\n        <li>**Product Knowledge Training:** Eggheads becomes a valuable tool for imparting in-depth product knowledge, ensuring that teams are well-versed in the offerings they present to clients.</li>\n        <li>**Customer Service Training:** Elevate customer service standards with targeted training modules, enhancing the skills of customer-facing teams.</li>\n        <li>**Compliance Training:** Eggheads plays a crucial role in compliance training, keeping teams informed and aligned with regulatory requirements.</li>\n    </ul>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Seamless Integration and Accessibility</h3>\n    <p>Eggheads\' flexibility extends to its accessibility, allowing users to access learning nuggets through a convenient link or the dedicated Microsoft Teams App. This seamless integration ensures that learning can happen anytime, anywhere.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Elevating Learning with AI</h3>\n    <p>At the heart of Eggheads is its AI-driven approach, enhancing the learning experience. The platform\'s ability to analyze user interactions and tailor learning nuggets accordingly ensures a personalized and effective learning journey.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Driving Business Success with Eggheads</h3>\n    <p>Eggheads not only imparts knowledge but becomes a catalyst for business success. Its impact on employee training, knowledge retention, and overall awareness positions it as a game-changer in the realm of microlearning.</p>\n</div>', 'Sales team training with easy conversational chatbot.\nEasy skills learning via conversations with AI assistant.\nRefresher training for improved learning retention.\nManage and improve employees training for better results.', 'https://eggheads.ai?via=studentaitools', NULL, 'https://eggheads.ai/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/circle_with_e2_249883264.svg', 'eggheads---ai-powered-microlearning-top.png', 'eggheads---ai-powered-microlearning-middle.png', 'eggheads---ai-powered-microlearning-bottom.png', 1, 0, 'free', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(74, 1, 'GistVid', 'gistvid', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Revolutionizing Learning with Gistvid: Transforming Videos into Interactive Educational Tools</h3>\n    <p>Gistvid emerges as a groundbreaking AI tool, reshaping the landscape of education by turning videos into interactive and enriching learning experiences. This innovative platform allows users to pose questions, receive instant answers, and interact with video content seamlessly, unlocking a new dimension of productivity.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Effortless Learning Acceleration with Gistvid</h3>\n    <p>Gistvid\'s core functionality lies in accelerating learning processes. By extracting valuable information from videos, it streamlines knowledge retrieval, saving users precious time. The ability to ask questions in real-time while watching videos is a game-changer, fostering a dynamic and engaging learning environment.</p>\n    <p>Furthermore, Gistvid serves as a repository of curiosity. Users can record their questions, ensuring that no query goes unanswered. This feature not only aids in information retention but also encourages continuous interaction with video content.</p>\n    <p>For collaborative learning, Gistvid offers the option to edit and collaborate on video summaries with colleagues. The sharing of links facilitates easy collaboration, enhancing the collective learning experience.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Unleashing the Power of Gistvid Features</h3>\n    <ul>\n        <li>**Rich Text Editor Integration:** Gistvid provides an integrated rich text editor, empowering users to work on blog posts or essays directly in the browser, seamlessly combining content creation and learning.</li>\n        <li>**Browser Extensions:** Enjoy the convenience of browser extensions for Firefox and Chrome, ensuring a smooth and accessible experience across different platforms.</li>\n        <li>**Unlimited Video Processing and Storage:** Gistvid removes limitations with unlimited video processing and storage directly in the browser, eliminating concerns about space constraints.</li>\n        <li>**Personalized Video Summaries:** Enhance organization with personalized video summaries featuring timestamps, allowing users to navigate content efficiently.</li>\n        <li>**Download Summaries as PDFs:** Gistvid offers the flexibility to download video summaries as PDFs, providing a portable and shareable format.</li>\n    </ul>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Enhanced Interactivity with Gistvid\'s Chat Interface</h3>\n    <p>Engage with video content through Gistvid\'s chat interface, asking questions and gaining insights based on the material. This interactive feature brings a social element to learning, allowing users to connect and learn together.</p>\n    <p>Access to a private API opens the door to premium features integration with other products and services, offering a tailored and comprehensive learning experience.</p>\n    <p>For seamless integration into websites and apps, Gistvid provides a JavaScript SDK, enabling easy one-line integration and extending the benefits of interactive learning to diverse online platforms.</p>\n</div>', 'N/A', 'https://gistvid.com/?via=studentaitools', NULL, NULL, 'gistvid-top.png', 'gistvid-middle.png', 'gistvid-bottom.png', 1, 0, 'free', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(75, 1, 'Qonqur', 'qonqur', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Qonqur: Elevating Presentations, Brainstorming, Learning, and Research</h3>\n    <p>Introducing Qonqur, the virtual hands control and mind mapping app that transcends traditional boundaries in presentations, brainstorming sessions, learning, and research. This innovative tool takes your experiences to the next level, ensuring engagement, creativity, and efficiency.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Revolutionize Presentations with Qonqur\'s Webcam Gesture Control</h3>\n    <p>Say goodbye to mundane presentations. Qonqur introduces an innovative webcam hand gesture control that captivates your audience\'s attention. No more sleep-inducing slides — Qonqur ensures your presentations are dynamic, interactive, and memorable.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Cool Ideas Galore: Brainstorming with Qonqur</h3>\n    <p>Unleash your creativity with Qonqur\'s cutting-edge features for brainstorming. It transforms the mundane into the extraordinary, making brainstorming sessions not just productive but downright cool. Generate, refine, and visualize ideas like never before.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Qonqur: A Learning Tool for the Future</h3>\n    <p>For students seeking a new learning frontier, Qonqur is the answer. This app unlocks knowledge and enhances the learning experience. Say goodbye to traditional methods; Qonqur introduces a dynamic, interactive approach to learning, making education exciting and effective.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Navigate Research with Ease Using Qonqur</h3>\n    <p>Research can be overwhelming, but not with Qonqur. This app is designed to help you make new discoveries and organize your ideas seamlessly. Say goodbye to information overload — Qonqur streamlines the research process, ensuring efficiency and clarity.</p>\n</div>', 'Enhancing presentations with innovative webcam hand gesture control.', 'https://qonqur.xyz/?via=studentaitools', NULL, 'https://qonqur.xyz/favicon.png', 'qonqur-top.png', 'qonqur-middle.png', 'qonqur-bottom.png', 1, 0, 'free', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(76, 1, 'Quetab', 'quetab', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Unveiling Quetab: Revolutionizing Learning through AI</h3>\n    <p>Quetab emerges as a modern AI-driven platform, a transformative force in boosting productivity, honing skills, and facilitating continuous learning through state-of-the-art technology.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Quetab Mobile App: Your Gateway to Swift Learning</h3>\n    <p>The Quetab mobile app is your companion in the quest for knowledge. Dive into flashcards, questions, and notes to accelerate your learning journey. The platform empowers users to generate custom questions and answers, simplifying the complexities of studying and test preparation.</p>\n    <p>Engage with the Quetab community by posing questions and tapping into a wealth of insights. This collaborative approach adds a dynamic layer to your learning experience.</p>\n    <p>Effortlessly create visual, audible, and textual notes to distill and summarize study material. Build a comprehensive collection that aligns with your unique learning style.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Diverse Study Sets for Holistic Learning</h3>\n    <p>Quetab opens doors to a vast collection of study sets spanning diverse subjects. Whether it\'s languages, science, life sciences, engineering, or beyond, Quetab ensures that there\'s something for every learner.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Monetize Your Expertise with Quetab</h3>\n    <p>One distinctive feature of Quetab is the opportunity to monetize your knowledge and skills. Share your valuable content on the platform and transform your expertise into a valuable resource. Quetab provides a platform for creators to reach a wider audience and derive tangible benefits from their contributions.</p>\n</div>', 'Efficient studying and test preparation.\nCollaborative learning and knowledge sharing.\nMonetising knowledge and skills.', 'https://www.quetab.com/?via=studentaitools', NULL, 'https://www.quetab.com/favicon.png', 'quetab-top.png', 'quetab-middle.png', 'quetab-bottom.png', 1, 0, 'free', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(77, 1, 'DUNNO', 'dunno', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Dunno: Revolutionizing Learning Through AI-Driven Quizzes</h3>\n    <p>Discover Dunno, the AI-powered quiz platform that reshapes the learning experience by transforming it into an engaging and interactive game. Whether you\'re an educator, tutor, or an individual on a self-learning journey, Dunno provides a platform to create quizzes and intellectual games effortlessly.</p>\n    <p>With Dunno, learning becomes a thrilling adventure. The platform enables users to generate quizzes with the assistance of AI, fostering engagement and deepening understanding. You have the flexibility to play solo or invite friends to join, making learning a social and enjoyable experience.</p>\n    <p>Moreover, Dunno extends its capabilities beyond traditional educational settings. Meetings, presentations, and events can be made more interactive by incorporating quizzes. The platform adds a fun element to social gatherings with friends and family by allowing users to create quizzes on a wide range of topics.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">The Power of AI Content Generation</h3>\n    <p>Dunno harnesses the capabilities of GPT-based models for content generation, ensuring accuracy and relevance in quizzes. Plans are underway to transition to the more advanced GPT-4 model, a testament to Dunno\'s commitment to staying at the forefront of AI technology.</p>\n    <p>While AI-generated content is known for its accuracy, Dunno emphasizes the importance of double-checking factual information. The platform prioritizes the integrity of information, recognizing the value of accurate and reliable educational content.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Enhancing Quizzing with ChatGPT Assistance</h3>\n    <p>For those seeking assistance in quiz creation, Dunno introduces ChatGPT, a helpful companion that generates prompts based on provided topics. Users can seamlessly integrate ChatGPT\'s insights into their quizzes, ensuring a diverse and engaging set of questions.</p>\n    <p>Once armed with answers from ChatGPT, users can launch games and invite others to participate. This collaborative and interactive approach adds a new dimension to the learning experience, making education not just informative but also enjoyable.</p>\n</div>', 'Create interactive quizzes for educational purposes.\nMake meetings and presentations more interactive with quizzes.\nEntertain and engage friends and family with quizzes.', 'https://www.dunno.gg/?via=studentaitools', NULL, 'https://static.wixstatic.com/shapes/0b9818_f037492c864f4705a9f15ef1310614ec.svg', 'dunno-top.png', 'dunno-middle.png', 'dunno-bottom.png', 1, 0, 'free', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(78, 1, 'Conker', 'conker', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Revolutionizing Assessments with Conker: An AI-Powered Quiz Creation Tool</h3>\n    <p>Conker stands as a beacon of innovation in the realm of education, offering an AI-powered quiz creation tool that simplifies the process of crafting assessments. Tailored for educators, Conker provides a diverse range of question types, allowing the customization of quizzes to meet the unique needs of students and accommodate different learning groups within a class.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Comprehensive Ready-Made Assessments for K-12</h3>\n    <p>Conker goes beyond basic quiz creation by offering thousands of ready-made, standards-aligned assessments for K-12 education. From NGSS to TEKS, educators can seamlessly integrate these assessments into their teaching, ensuring alignment with curriculum standards and saving valuable preparation time.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Accessibility and Accommodations</h3>\n    <p>Conker is committed to accessibility, offering accommodations such as integrated read-aloud to support students with diverse needs. This commitment ensures that every student can engage with assessments in a way that suits their learning style.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Effortless Integration and Sharing</h3>\n    <p>Conker simplifies the sharing and integration of quizzes by allowing easy export to Google Forms. Teachers can seamlessly share assessments on Canvas LMS, enhancing convenience for educators using these platforms. The integration with Google Forms opens up a world of possibilities, enabling teachers to challenge and stimulate students with a variety of question types effortlessly generated by Conker.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Maximizing Teaching Time with Automation</h3>\n    <p>Conker doesn\'t just create quizzes; it automates the entire process, saving educators time and ensuring fast, accurate results. This automation empowers teachers to focus more on instruction and less on administrative tasks, ultimately enhancing the teaching experience.</p>\n    <p>Furthermore, Conker aligns seamlessly with popular learning management systems like Canvas. This integration allows educators to utilize Conker\'s capabilities across multiple platforms, providing flexibility and convenience in quiz creation and management.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">A Trusted Ally in Curriculum-Aligned Teaching</h3>\n    <p>By using Conker, educators can align their teaching with curriculum standards, confident in the knowledge that there\'s a comprehensive standards-aligned quiz bank at their disposal. This not only simplifies the planning process but also ensures that assessments are in sync with educational objectives.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Unlocking Possibilities with Seamless Integration</h3>\n    <p>Conker goes beyond being a quiz creation tool; it\'s a key that unlocks possibilities for teaching. Its seamless integration with popular learning management systems enhances its usability, making it a versatile tool for educators looking to create, share, and manage quizzes with ease.</p>\n</div>', 'N/A', 'https://conker.ai/?via=studentaitools', NULL, 'https://framerusercontent.com/images/XvUUejVGzayi2WCQPIScZiDcytQ.png', 'conker-top.png', 'conker-middle.png', 'conker-bottom.png', 1, 0, 'free', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(79, 1, 'Tutor AI', 'tutor-ai', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Exploring Speak English AI: Revolutionizing Language Learning</h3>\n    <p>Tutor AI introduces Speak English AI, an advanced English-speaking tutor powered by artificial intelligence. This groundbreaking application is meticulously designed to assist individuals in enhancing their spoken English skills within a safe and judgment-free environment.</p>\n    <p>Speak English AI opens the door to free-flowing and natural conversations, allowing users to interact with a diverse range of AI characters. Each character boasts unique traits such as gender, age, accent, and profession, creating a dynamic and immersive language learning experience.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Key Features of Speak English AI</h3>\n    <ul>\n        <li>**Diverse AI Characters:** Engage in conversations with AI characters featuring distinct characteristics, providing a varied and realistic language practice environment.</li>\n        <li>**Real-time Feedback:** Speak English AI evaluates the user\'s language in real-time, offering valuable feedback to enhance spoken English skills. Users receive suggestions for better expressions and alternatives, fostering continuous improvement.</li>\n        <li>**Vocabulary Expansion:** The application serves as a tool for vocabulary expansion, helping users refine their communication style and express themselves more effectively.</li>\n        <li>**Adjustable Features:** Tailor the learning experience with adjustable features. Slow down the speed of conversations for a more focused approach, and access word-for-word translations or complete message translations with a simple click.</li>\n    </ul>\n</div>', 'Improve spoken English skills.\nEnhance vocabulary and communication style.\nTrack progress and achieve language goals.', 'https://www.speakenglishwithai.com/?via=studentaitools', NULL, NULL, 'tutor-ai-top.png', 'tutor-ai-middle.png', 'tutor-ai-bottom.png', 1, 0, 'free', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(80, 1, 'Resoomer', 'resoomer', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Resoomer: Navigating the Seas of Information Overload</h3>\n    <p>In an age dominated by information overload, Resoomer emerges as a transformative solution, reshaping how we engage with textual content. This platform serves as a virtual window to vast knowledge, offering in-depth analysis and comprehension that is essential for students, professionals, and avid readers alike.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Key Attributes of Resoomer</h3>\n    <ul>\n        <li>**Intelligent Synthesis:** Resoomer employs intelligent synthesis to extract core insights from dense content, providing users with a concise yet comprehensive understanding.</li>\n        <li>**Automated Summarization:** The platform excels in automated summarization, allowing users to save time by swiftly obtaining condensed summaries of lengthy texts.</li>\n        <li>**Citation Identification:** Resoomer goes beyond mere summarization by identifying and preserving essential citations, ensuring accuracy and credibility.</li>\n        <li>**Browser Integration:** Seamlessly integrate Resoomer into your browsing experience, making it a versatile tool for online research and reading.</li>\n        <li>**Customizable Summaries:** Tailor your reading experience with Resoomer\'s customizable summaries, adapting the tool to your specific needs and preferences.</li>\n        <li>**Multilingual Support:** Resoomer breaks language barriers with its multilingual support, making it a globally accessible platform for users worldwide.</li>\n    </ul>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Universal Access with Resoomer</h3>\n    <p>One of Resoomer\'s standout features is its commitment to universal access. The platform is accessible free of charge, ensuring that its benefits are available to everyone. No registration is needed, enhancing usability and eliminating barriers to entry.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Beyond Summarization: Resoomer as Your Reading Ally</h3>\n    <p>Resoomer transcends the conventional boundaries of text summarization. It becomes a valuable reading ally, saving time and enhancing understanding amidst the deluge of information. By offering condensed yet insightful summaries, Resoomer becomes an indispensable tool for navigating the vast sea of information.</p>\n</div>', 'Efficient summarization for students\' research materials.\nQuick insights extraction for professionals dealing with lengthy documents.\nConcise content review for readers navigating information-rich articles.', 'https://resoomer.com/en/?via=studentaitools', NULL, NULL, 'resoomer-top.png', 'resoomer-middle.png', 'resoomer-bottom.png', 1, 0, 'free', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(81, 1, 'Bloom', 'bloom', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Meet \"Bloom\": Redefining Education with GPT-4 Power</h3>\n    <p>Embark on a revolutionary learning journey with \"Bloom,\" an innovative learning companion that transcends the boundaries of traditional education. Fueled by the powerful GPT-4, Bloom introduces a new era of education by engaging users in unique conversations that foster insightful learning experiences.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Unleashing the Power of GPT-4</h3>\n    <p>Bloom is not just a learning companion; it\'s a dynamic platform powered by the state-of-the-art GPT-4. This default integration ensures that every interaction with Bloom is not just educational but also intellectually stimulating. From 1:1 tutoring to group study and classroom activities, Bloom leverages the advanced capabilities of GPT-4 to deliver unparalleled learning experiences.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Your Digital Campus: Bloom on Discord</h3>\n    <p>Engage with Bloom seamlessly on Discord, your digital campus for learning. Whether you seek personalized tutoring, collaborative group study, or interactive classroom activities, Bloom on Discord is your go-to destination. The platform is accessible for free on both desktop and mobile, ensuring that learning is not bound by location or device.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Crafting Safe and Personalized Learning Experiences</h3>\n    <p>Bloom is more than just an AI tool; it\'s a creation by students for students and tech-focused companies. The platform seamlessly blends AI expertise with pedagogical practices to deliver a safe, personalized, and highly effective learning environment. Moderation features ensure a secure space for learning, and Bloom\'s commitment to holistic education embraces the humanities.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Join the Revolution: Bloom on Private Discord Servers</h3>\n    <p>Bloom isn\'t confined to public spaces. Experience the revolution by adding Bloom to your private Discord servers. This feature enhances the versatility of Bloom, making it a valuable addition to various educational settings. Try it now to elevate and boost your learning experience.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Revolutionize Learning with Bloom</h3>\n    <p>Bloom invites you to revolutionize your learning journey. Its unique blend of AI intelligence, student-centric design, and commitment to holistic education sets it apart. Join Discord, meet Bloom, and witness a new era in education. Don\'t miss the opportunity to enhance your learning experience with Bloom\'s powerful capabilities.</p>\n</div>', 'Personalized tutoring for students that is powered by AI.\nGroup study and collaboration via discord servers.\nCreate classroom activities and assignments to improve the learning experience.', 'https://bloombot.ai/?via=studentaitools', NULL, 'https://bloombot.ai/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/bloom-fav-icon@10x-66x66.png', 'bloom-top.png', 'bloom-middle.png', 'bloom-bottom.png', 1, 0, 'free', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(82, 1, 'AcademicHelp AI Writer', 'academichelp-ai-writer', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Unlocking the Potential of AcademicHelp AI Writer</h3>\n    <p>AcademicHelp AI Writer emerges as a supercharged, free AI essay writer, revolutionizing the landscape of academic writing. This advanced tool goes beyond conventional essay generators, offering a suite of features designed to streamline the writing process.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Features That Define AcademicHelp AI Writer</h3>\n    <ul>\n        <li>**Scholarly Sources:** Benefit from an extensive database of scholarly sources to enhance the credibility of your essays.</li>\n        <li>**MLA/APA Citations:** AcademicHelp AI Writer takes care of citation requirements, providing MLA/APA citations backed by solid evidence.</li>\n        <li>**Essay Generation:** Effortlessly generate essays based on provided topics, saving time and effort in the research and writing process.</li>\n        <li>**Content Organization:** Seamlessly organize content within your essays, ensuring a logical flow and coherence.</li>\n        <li>**Outline Creation:** AcademicHelp AI Writer aids in creating comprehensive outlines, serving as a roadmap for your academic work.</li>\n        <li>**Citation Variety:** Cater to diverse citation styles, including APA, MLA, and more, with the tool\'s versatile citation generation capabilities.</li>\n        <li>**User-Friendly Interface:** Experience the convenience of a user-friendly interface, requiring only basic inputs to generate complete and well-structured essays.</li>\n    </ul>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Versatility for Every Essay Type</h3>\n    <p>AcademicHelp AI Writer stands out by accommodating various essay types, adapting to the unique requirements of descriptive, argumentative, narrative, persuasive, compare and contrast, and expository essays.</p>\n    <p>Whether you\'re a high school student or pursuing higher education, this tool is tailored to simplify the academic writing journey at every level.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Save Time, Elevate Your Writing</h3>\n    <p>The generated content from AcademicHelp AI Writer serves as an invaluable starting point for academic assignments. By automating research and citation processes, the tool empowers users to save time and channel their efforts into refining their writing.</p>\n</div>', 'Quickly generate essays for academic assignments.\nOrganize and structure content for research papers.\nAssist with generating citations in different styles.', 'https://academichelp.net/free-essay-generator/?via=studentaitools', NULL, 'https://academichelp.net/favicon.svg', 'academichelp-ai-writer-top.png', 'academichelp-ai-writer-middle.png', 'academichelp-ai-writer-bottom.png', 1, 0, 'free', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(83, 1, 'Coursable.io', 'coursable.io', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Exploring Coursable: Your Personal AI Study Assistant</h3>\n    <p>Coursable emerges as a revolutionary personal AI study assistant, simplifying the initiation of learning new topics by generating personalized courses from approved study materials found on the web. Whether your academic curiosity leads you to explore data structures or entirely new subjects, Coursable stands ready to craft a customized guide tailored to your learning needs.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Seamless Learning with Coursable</h3>\n    <p>Using Coursable is a straightforward process. Simply communicate your desired subject of study, and Coursable takes charge, adjusting the course to match your unique needs. It scours the web for approved study materials, evaluates their quality, and presents you with an optimal course to kickstart your learning journey.</p>\n    <p>What sets Coursable apart is its adaptability. You have the power to request changes to further optimize the course, ensuring it aligns precisely with what you want to learn. This flexibility makes Coursable an invaluable tool for individuals initiating research, seeking a general understanding of a subject, or preparing for advanced online courses.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Your Personalized Education Booster</h3>\n    <p>Coursable acts as a potent booster to your education, capable of substituting a professionally taught course. It brings the benefits of personal one-on-one education directly to you, customized to your preferences and learning style.</p>\n    <p>Once you confirm your course, Coursable opens the door to a wealth of materials and provides a structured course outline. This allows you to learn at your own pace, monitor your progress, and even share the curated course as a PDF.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Key Features of Coursable</h3>\n    <ul>\n        <li>**Personalized Learning:** Enjoy a tailored learning experience that adapts to your unique preferences and requirements.</li>\n        <li>**Course Optimization:** Request changes to the course to make it precisely what you want to learn.</li>\n        <li>**Material Access:** Gain access to a curated selection of approved study materials from the web.</li>\n        <li>**Flexible Learning Pace:** Learn at your own pace, tracking progress and ensuring a comprehensive understanding.</li>\n        <li>**Course Sharing:** Share your personalized course as a PDF, fostering collaborative learning experiences.</li>\n    </ul>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">In Summary, Coursable: Your Gateway to Personalized Learning</h3>\n    <p>Coursable is not just an AI tool; it\'s your companion in the journey of personalized learning. From kickstarting your learning adventure to providing curated courses tailored to your needs, Coursable is the key to unlocking a world of knowledge.</p>\n</div>', 'Start learning a new subject with personalized learning plans.\nGain a general understanding of a topic quickly.\nCreate online courses easily on different topics.\nGenerate Curated course materials for a topic of interest.', 'https://coursable.io/?via=studentaitools', NULL, 'https://coursable.io/favicon.ico', 'coursable.io-top.png', 'coursable.io-middle.png', 'coursable.io-bottom.png', 1, 0, 'free', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(84, 1, 'Tech-treks.com', 'tech-treks.com', NULL, '<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Unlocking the World of Technology: Your AI-Powered Guide</h3>\n    <p>Embark on a journey of tech exploration with our all-encompassing resource designed for individuals at every expertise level. Whether you\'re a beginner, intermediate, or an expert, our AI-powered platform is your gateway to a deeper understanding of diverse technologies.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">AI-Driven Learning Paths</h3>\n    <p>Our resource stands out with AI-powered learning paths that cater to various proficiency levels. From comprehensive crash courses to engaging code challenges, it\'s a dynamic learning experience that adapts to your skill level.</p>\n    <p>Explore curated code snippets that offer practical insights into real-world applications. Our platform goes beyond theory, providing hands-on experiences that resonate with the demands of the tech industry.</p>\n    <p>Prepare for interviews with confidence using our Q&A roadmaps. Our AI-driven approach ensures that you cover essential topics and gain the knowledge needed to succeed in technical interviews.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-group\">\n    <h3 class=\"title-animation fw-6 text-white mt-12\">Diverse Resources Tailored for You</h3>\n    <ul>\n        <li>**Crash Courses:** Dive into intensive crash courses designed to fast-track your understanding of key technologies.</li>\n        <li>**Code Challenges:** Sharpen your coding skills with a variety of challenges that keep learning engaging and dynamic.</li>\n        <li>**Code Snippets:** Access curated snippets that bridge the gap between theoretical knowledge and practical application.</li>\n        <li>**Interview Preparation:** Navigate the complexities of technical interviews with our comprehensive Q&A roadmaps.</li>\n        <li>**And More:** Our platform is a 