(85, 1, 'Conversly', 'conversly', NULL, 'Conversly is a language learning app that allows you to practice and improve your conversational skills in a new language.With this app, you can practice speaking, listening, and even translate sentences using advanced AI-powered technology.Engage in conversations with various characters and choose from four different conversing modes to suit your learning style.Whether you\'re preparing for a trip to Spain or trying to communicate better with friends in French, Conversly can help you feel more comfortable and confident.It\'s like having a 24/7 language exchange partner in your pocket, offering useful corrections and guidance.You can even take turns with the AI to create stories and review your mistakes with just a single tap.', 'Practice language speaking and listening skills.\nImprove conversational skills in any language.\nGet language lessons from an AI coach.\nUse as a translation companion on your next trip.', 'https://www.conversly.ai/?via=studentaitools', NULL, 'https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6423d2ce6c3ec43a23974159/b8ca8b2e-2352-494b-a8d9-08df58b2c7ed/favicon.ico', 'conversly-top.png', 'conversly-middle.png', 'conversly-bottom.png', 1, 0, 'free', NULL, NULL, NULL);
